{"type":"message","id":"bb4f39f1","parentId":"926b83f9","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:56:17.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. According to my instructions, I need to run a Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding. Let me check what files I need to read:\n\n1. MEMORY.md - This is already in the project context and loaded\n2. I should check if there are any other required startup files\n\nLooking at the workspace files injected:\n- AGENTS.md\n- SOUL.md\n- TOOLS.md\n- IDENTITY.md\n- USER.md\n- HEARTBEAT.md\n- BOOTSTRAP.md (missing)\n- MEMORY.md\n\nThese are already loaded in the Project Context above. So I have what I need.\n\nNow I need to greet the user in my configured persona. Looking at SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md, they're mostly empty templates. But I have some info from MEMORY.md:\n- The user's name is \"小八\" (from the memory about 小六 and 小八)\n- My name is 小六 (from MEMORY.md: \"小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\" and \"小六的 emoji 是 🦐\")\n\nWait, let me re-read the context more carefully. In MEMORY.md it says:\n- \"关于小八: 小八的名字是小八, 小八位于北京\"\n- \"关于小六 (AI): 小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手, 小六的 emoji 是 🦐\"\n\nSo I'm 小六 (Xiao Liu), and the user is 小八 (Xiao Ba). My emoji is 🦐.\n\nI should greet them in a friendly, casual way - be myself. Keep it 1-3 sentences, mention the model if it differs from default.\n\nLooking at the runtime info:\n- model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n\n\n- default_model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n\nThey're the same, so no need to mention it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHey 小八！🦐 晚上好～新会话已就绪，今晚有什么我可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":13794,"output":415,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14209,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775400971059,"responseId":"chatcmpl-74b8c673-9091-45b7-b7de-6477490955b2"}}
