{"type":"message","id":"c2e92b56","parentId":"4f1eb72a","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:02:07.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来服务启动了，但是返回了 401 未授权错误。这是因为 OpenClaw Gateway 可能有认证保护。\n\n让我检查一下 openclaw-router 是否也能正常启动。但首先我需要修复 context-api 的认证问题。\n\n让我先停止后台进程，然后重新测试。实际上，401 可能是因为curl需要通过网关的认证。让我先检查一下 openclaw-router 能否启动。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_60570848603e4861988ad08e","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"calm-haven"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":22600,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22712,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775401325805,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3c5e4426-2725-40de-b1a9-65c0d8e0170a"}}
