{"type":"message","id":"9d1abcf8","parentId":"8935dc10","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:12:44.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建 SKILL.md\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5e33d6788384ba2236aace346b68","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Task Orchestrator 技能\n\n> 全自动任务编排：评分路由 + 上下文保护 + 子代理进度上报\n\n## 功能\n\n- **评分路由**: 根据任务复杂度自动选择执行模式 (DIRECT / STEP_ARCHIVE / SPAWN_SUBAGENT / MEGA_TASK)\n- **上下文保护**: 自动压缩会话历史，避免上下文溢出\n- **子代理进度**: 实时上报子代理执行进度\n\n## 执行模式\n\n| 分数 | 模式 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s |\n\n## 评分因子\n\n- 指令数量\n- 代码行数\n- 依赖复杂度\n- CPU/IO/网络 强度\n- 预估执行时间","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7849,"output":268,"cacheRead":22144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775401944902,"responseId":"019d5e33c3cea3fd5817b21ad0b47711"}}
