{"type":"message","id":"b9339eac","parentId":"4fc2f2f6","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:13:11.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5e33b1ece89ac0c8e92d93b99154","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Config warnings ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                          │\n│  - plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config)  │\n│    but config is present                                                 │\n│                                                                          │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\nSkills (32/69 ready)\n┌───────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────┐\n│ Status        │ Skill                               │ Description                               │ Source             │\n├───────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────┤\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-doc                       │ Feishu document read/write operations.    │ openclaw-extra     │\n│               │                                     │ Activate when user mentions Feishu docs,  │                    │\n│               │                                     │ cloud docs, or docx links.                │                    │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-drive                     │ Feishu cloud storage file management.     │ openclaw-extra     │\n│               │                                     │ Activate when user mentions cloud space,  │                    │\n│               │                                     │ folders, drive.                           │                    │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-perm                      │ Feishu permission