aya` to list, read, write, reply,   │                    │\n│               │                                     │ forward, search, and organize emails      │                    │\n│               │                                     │ from the terminal. Supports multiple      │                    │\n│               │                                     │ accounts and message composition with     │                    │\n│               │                                     │ MML (MIME Meta Language).                 │                    │\n│ △ needs setup │ 📨 imsg                             │ iMessage/SMS CLI for listing chats,       │ openclaw-bundled   │\n│               │                                     │ history, and sending messages via         │                    │\n│               │                                     │ Messages.app.                             │                    │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 mcporter                         │ Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure,  │ openclaw-bundled   │\n│               │                                     │ auth, and call MCP servers/tools          │                    │\n│               │                                     │ directly (HTTP or stdio), including ad-   │                    │\n│               │                                     │ hoc servers, config edits, and CLI/type   │                    │\n│               │                                     │ generation.                               │                    │\n│ △ needs setup │ 📊 model-usage                      │ Use CodexBar CLI local cost usage to      │ openclaw-bundled   │\n│               │                                     │ summarize per-model usage for Codex or    │                    │\n│               │                                     │ Claude, including the current (most       │                    │\n│               │                                     │ recent) model or a full model breakdown.  │              