{"type":"message","id":"f7526c2b","parentId":"e98610d5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:18:15.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提醒的对！之前我们创建的反向代理中间件应该可以拦截任务并进行评分路由。这才是 task_orchestrator 的真正用途 —— 通过中间件拦截任务、自动评分、自动选择执行模式。\n\n让我检查一下中间件服务是否在运行，然后测试一下它的功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对！中间件已经在运行了。让我测试反向代理中间件的拦截和评分功能：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5e391357df11470ebc14d99296b8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3102/health"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12345,"output":108,"cacheRead":28416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40869,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775402285842,"responseId":"019d5e38f585d1b3f4163dcf284e438b"}}
