{"type":"message","id":"2392a238","parentId":"a164d49c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:19:04.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's an error in the scorer. The factors.scaleIndex is undefined. Looking at my scoring.js code, scaleIndex is always set to 1 in the simplified version. Let me check the scoring.js to confirm and fix it.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5e3935281dd84ba4c6f090633335","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/scoring.js","limit":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":513,"output":89,"cacheRead":41984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775402339246,"responseId":"019d5e3927bddf9b40eb735fea135f15"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e2bc753","parentId":"2392a238","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:19:04.591Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5e3935281dd84ba4c6f090633335","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// scoring.js\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.10, codeLines: 0.08, dependencyComplexity: 0.12,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10, ioIntensity: 0.08, networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.15, scaleIndex: 0.25\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n // 简化版，实际可扩展\n const factors = {\n instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n codeLines: 1,\n dependencyComplexity: /npm|pip|install/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gzip/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n ioIntensity: /cp|mv|tar|dd/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n networkIntensity: /curl|wget|git clone/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n estimatedDuration: /sleep|compile|backup/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n scaleIndex: 1\n };\n let weighted = 0;\n for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(factors)) weighted += v * WEIGHTS[k];\n\n[14 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775402344584}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d8c4f6b","parentId":"1e2bc753","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:19:10.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scoring.js looks correct. The issue is that computeFineScore returns {totalScore, factors}, but factors contains scaleIndex. Let me check the router code where the error occurs - line 38 is:\n```javascript\nconst plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors.scaleIndex);\n```\n\nWait, the function is `computeFineScore` which returns `{ totalScore, factors }`. But the problem is that computeFineScore is an async function but we're not awaiting it. Let me fix that.\n\nActually wait - looking more carefully at the error:\n```\nTypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'scaleIndex')\n```\n\nThis suggests `score.factors` is undefined. That means `computeFineScore` is being called but not awaited, so we're getting a Promise instead of the actual result. Let me fix the router code.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fe9f22f4a9534457a7f93189","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"app.get('/api/score', async (req, res) => {\n  const taskSpec = req.query.task || '';\n  const score = await computeFineScore(taskSpec);\n  const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n  res.json({ score, plan });\n});","oldText":"app.get('/api/score', (req, res) => {\n  const taskSpec = req.query.task || '';\n  const score = computeFineScore(taskSpec);\n  const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors.scaleIndex);\n  res.json({ score, plan });\n});"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":42965,"output":369,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17754023