{"type":"message","id":"382bab0e","parentId":"af53dcbb","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:20:27.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The task orchestrator is now working correctly. Let me summarize the results:\n\n| 任务类型 | 任务示例 | 分数 | 执行模式 |\n|----------|----------|------|----------|\n| 简单 | `ls` | 20 | DIRECT (30s) |\n| 中等 | `ls -la && pwd` | 22 | STEP_ARCHIVE (60s) |\n| 复杂 | `npm install && make && make test` | 35 | STEP_ARCHIVE (60s) |\n| 超大 | git clone + npm install + make test | 44 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT (132s) |\n\nThe task orchestrator is working! Now I should tell the user about the results.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n✅ **任务编排系统完全生效！**\n\n| 任务示例 | 分数 | 执行模式 | 超时 |\n|----------|------|----------|------|\n| `ls` | 20 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| `ls -la && pwd` | 22 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| `npm install && make && make test` | 35 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| `git clone + npm install + make test` | 44 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 132s |\n\n反向代理中间件 `3102` 端口正在自动：\n1. **拦截任务** → 分析 taskSpec\n2. **计算分数** → 评估复杂度/依赖/CPU/IO/网络\n3. **选择模式** → DIRECT / STEP_ARCHIVE / SPAWN_SUBAGENT / MEGA_TASK\n4. **返回执行计划** → 包含超时和内存限制\n\n现在需要配置 systemd 服务使用新代码，或者手动重启服务。要我帮你更新 systemd 服务吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":45463,"output":368,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45831,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402421613,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8cf7e14c-35af-42e6-9cd4-756e6a9c48be"}}
