{"type":"message","id":"44185354","parentId":"3daa0dff","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:36:49.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0398bb474f3448e7b90f33ce","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== AGENTS.md 规则 ===\n# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 任务执行前必做：复杂度评估\n\n收到任何任务请求时，**必须先使用 task_orchestrator 进行自动评分**，再根据分数选择执行策略：\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|----------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n评分因子：\n- 指令数量 (instructionCount)\n- 代码行数 (codeLines)\n- 依赖复杂度 (dependencyComplexity)\n- CPU 强度 (cpuIntensity)\n- IO 强度 (ioIntensity)\n- 网络强度 (networkIntensity)\n- 预估执行时间 (estimatedDuration)\n- 规模指数 (scaleIndex)\n\n### 子代理进度上报 (v2.0)\n\nspawn 子代理时复用进度上报机制：\n- 子代理输出 `[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>` 格式\n- 主代理捕获 stdout 解析进度标记，限流转发给用户 (1条/秒)\n- 心跳：30秒无输出发送\"仍在运行\"\n- 无产出检测：30秒无输出 → 警告 → 强制终止\n- 相关配置：SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB, PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS 等\n\n### 任务编排器 (task_orchestrator v3.0)\n\n整合三大能力：\n1. **任务评分路由**: 多维度评分 → DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/PARALLEL_SHARDS/MEGA_TASK\n2. **上下文保护**: 消息数≥50 或 字符≥100KB 或 token≥80% → 自动压缩写入记忆\n3. **子代理进度上报**: 同上 v2.0\n\n技能文件: \n- `~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/` (核心代码)\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/` (工作区副本)\n\n中间件:\n- Router: `localhost:3102` (任务评分 + 反向代理)\n\n=== scoring.js 规则 ===\n// scoring.js\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.10, codeLines: 0.08, dependencyComplexity: 0.12,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10, ioIntensity: 0.08, networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.15, scaleIndex: 0.25\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n // 简化版，实际可扩展\n const factors = {\n instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n codeLines: 1,\n dependencyComplexity: /npm|pip|install/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gzip/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n ioIntensity: /cp|mv|tar|dd/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n networkIntensity: /curl|wget|git clone/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n estimatedDuration: /sleep|compile|backup/.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n scaleIndex: 1\n };\n let weighted = 0;\n for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(factors)) weighted += v * WEIGHTS[k];\n const totalScore = Math.min(100, Math.round(weighted * 20));\n return { totalScore, factors };\n}\n\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, score * 3), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, score * 2), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'DISTRIBUTED', message: 'Too complex' };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan };"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"=== AGENTS.md 规则 ===\n# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 任务执行前必做：复杂度评估\n\n收到任何任务请求时，**必须先使用 task_orchestrator 进行自动评分**，再根据分数选择执行策略：\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|----------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n评分因子：\n- 指令数量 (instructionCount)\n- 代码行数 (codeLines)\n- 依赖复杂度 (dependencyComplexity)\n- CPU 强度 (cpuIntensity)\n- IO 强度 (ioIntensity)\n- 网