{"type":"message","id":"289e786c","parentId":"7577f3fc","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:39:46.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求再次检查。我需要系统性地检查所有配置是否正确对齐。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5e4c79664cb2cba61253af7ab22f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 1. AGENTS.md 规则 ===\" \ngrep -A 10 \"分数.*执行方式\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 2. scoring.js 执行计划 ===\" \ngrep -A 8 \"getExecutionPlan\" ~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/scoring.js\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3. 中间件评分测试 ===\" \necho \"简单任务 (ls):\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=ls\" | jq -r '.plan.mode, .plan.timeoutSec'\necho \"中等任务 (npm install && make):\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=npm%20install%20%26%26%20make\" | jq -r '.plan.mode, .plan.timeoutSec'\necho \"复杂任务 (多步骤):\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=git%20clone%20%26%26%20npm%20install%20%26%26%20make%20%26%26%20make%20test%20%26%26%20make%20dist\" | jq -r '.plan.mode, .plan.timeoutSec'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 4. 服务状态 ===\" \nsystemctl is-active openclaw-router openclaw-context\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 5. 配置文件 ===\" \nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md ~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md ~/.openclaw/.env ~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/scoring.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2927,"output":385,"cacheRead":58496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61808,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775403562155,"responseId":"019d5e4c6c95b56b571c35e15e883b62"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8641962d","parentId":"289e786c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:39:46.606Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5e4c79664cb2cba61253af7ab22f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 1. AGENTS.md 规则 ===\n\n=== 2. scoring.js 执行计划 ===\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan };\n\n=== 3. 中间件评分测试 ===\n简单任务 (ls):\nDIRECT\n30\n中等任务 (npm install && make):\nSTEP_ARCHIVE\nnull\n复杂任务 (多步骤):\nSPAWN_SUBAGENT\n132\n\n=== 4. 服务状态 ===\nactive\nactivating\n\n=== 5. 配置文件 ===\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai  180 Apr  5 23:28 /home/ai/.openclaw/.env\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai 1765 Apr  5 23:37 /home/ai/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/scoring.js\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai 1980 Apr  5 23:27 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai  671 Apr  5 23:28 /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":87,"aggregated":"=== 1. AGENTS.md 规则 ===\n\n=== 2. scoring.js 执行计划 ===\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (