{"type":"message","id":"54dc432b","parentId":"0f0f082f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:40:16.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来评分机制的最高分只能到55左右，因为scaleIndex固定为1。让我检查一下规则对齐情况：1. AGENTS.md 和 scoring.js 已经对齐\n2. 问题：当前任务复杂度评分最高只能到55-60左右，无法触发61-80的PARALLEL_SHARDS或>80的MEGA_TASK\n\n这可能需要调整评分权重或者添加手动触发MEGA_TASK的方式。\n\n让我给用户一个总结报告：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 📋 最终检查报告\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| AGENTS.md vs scoring.js | ✅ 对齐 | 规则一致 |\n| DIRECT (≤20) | ✅ | 30s |\n| STEP_ARCHIVE (21-40) | ✅ | 60s, 1024MB |\n| SPAWN_SUBAGENT (41-60) | ✅ | 60-180s, 2048MB |\n| PARALLEL_SHARDS (61-80) | ⚠️ 未触发 | 最高分约55 |\n| MEGA_TASK (>80) | ⚠️ 未触发 | 需scaleIndex≥4 |\n\n## ⚠️ 潜在问题\n\n当前评分算法最高只能到约 **55-60 分**，无法触发 **PARALLEL_SHARDS** 或 **MEGA_TASK**。\n\n**解决方案**：\n1. 调整 `scoring.js` 权重提高总分\n2. 或允许手动指定 `scaleIndex >= 4` 触发 MEGA_TASK\n\n需要调整评分算法吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":63456,"output":315,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775403611720,"responseId":"chatcmpl-94802fec-07ba-4827-b57c-0f717dc29317"}}
