{"type":"message","id":"9dcbc594","parentId":"a833e37e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:46:01.447Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5e519406a5a20738e88d2d67f479","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║           规则对照检查: AGENTS.md vs scoring.js               ║\n╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 1. 评分因子对照                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\nAGENTS.md 定义:          scoring.js 实现:\n---\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 2. 执行模式对照                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|----------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n---\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 3. 实际测试                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n任务                                        分数   执行模式      \n---                                           ---      ---               \nls                                            22       STEP_ARCHIVE      \nnpm install && make                           43       SPAWN_SUBAGENT    \ngit clone && npm install && make test         63       PARALLEL_SHARDS   \ndocker build && make all && terraform apply   55       MEGA_TASK         \n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 4. 配置文件状态                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\nsystemd 服务: active activating\nRouter 端口: 1 个监听\nContext 端口: 1 个监听\n/home/ai/.openclaw/.env 180\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md 1980\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md 671"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":260,"aggregated":"╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║           规则对照检查: AGENTS.md vs scoring.js               ║\n╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 1. 评分因子对照                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\nAGENTS.md 定义:          scoring.js 实现:\n---\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 2. 执行模式对照                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|----------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n---\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 3. 实际测试                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n任务                                        分数   执行模式      \n---                                           ---      ---               \nls                                            22       STEP_ARCHIVE      \nnpm install && make                           43       SPAWN_SUBAGENT    \ngit clone && npm install && make test         63       PARALLEL_SHARDS   \ndocker build && make all && terraform apply   55       MEGA_TASK         \n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 4. 配置文件状态                                             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\nsystemd 服务: active activating\nRouter 端口: 1 个监听\nContext 端口: 1 个监听\n/home/ai/.openclaw/.env 180\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md 1980\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md 671","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775403961438}}
