{"type":"message","id":"9c8af1c0","parentId":"a2d66f46","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:49:51.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说不需要将技能注册到官方列表。那当前的实现已经完成了。让我做一个最终总结确认。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，当前实现已经完整：\n\n## ✅ 任务编排系统已就绪\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Router 中间件 (3102) | ✅ 评分+路由 |\n| Context API (3101) | ✅ 上下文管理 |\n| scoring.js | ✅ 多维度评分 |\n| progress_reporter.js | ✅ 进度上报 |\n| context_protector.js | ✅ 上下文保护 |\n| systemd 服务 | ✅ 自动启动 |\n| AGENTS.md 规则 | ✅ 已同步 |\n\n系统通过中间件方式自动拦截任务、评分、选择执行模式，无需额外配置。\n\n还有其他需要检查的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":73474,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73628,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775404188320,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a85db349-59e5-4ea8-874f-2b26c09a4e93"}}
