{"type":"message","id":"89d5ef1d","parentId":"c313983d","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:50:08.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要了解这个任务编排系统的介绍。让我总结一下整个系统的功能和架构。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 🦐 Task Orchestrator v3.0 任务编排系统\n\n### 核心功能\n\n**1. 智能评分路由**\n- 自动分析任务复杂度（8个维度）\n- 根据分数选择最佳执行模式\n\n**2. 执行模式**\n\n| 模式 | 场景 | 超时 | 内存 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| DIRECT | 简单命令 | 30s | - |\n| STEP_ARCHIVE | 中等任务 | 60s | 1GB |\n| SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 复杂任务 | 180s | 2GB |\n| PARALLEL_SHARDS | 大型任务 | 160s | 2GB |\n| MEGA_TASK | 超大任务 | 2h | 8GB |\n\n**3. 评分因子**\n- 指令数量、代码行数\n- 依赖复杂度\n- CPU/IO/网络强度\n- 预估执行时间\n- 规模指数（scaleIndex）\n\n### 架构\n\n```\n用户任务 → Router:3102 → scoring.js → 执行计划 → 执行\n                ↓\n         Context API:3101 (上下文保护)\n```\n\n### 使用方式\n\n```bash\n# 评分查询\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=ls\"\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=docker%20build%20%26%26%20make%20all\"\n\n# 任务提交\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/task \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"taskSpec\":\"npm install && make test\"}'\n```\n\n有问题随时问！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":73665,"output":365,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74030,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775404202792,"responseId":"chatcmpl-37e315ce-a972-4300-a590-30617fa577b1"}}
