{"type":"message","id":"06d61f5a","parentId":"c2aefb45","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:59:10.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经回答了用户的问题。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nClaude Code 使用 **Anthropic Claude 模型**：\n\n| 模型 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Sonnet 4** | 默认，平衡性能与速度 |\n| Opus 4 | 高性能，适合复杂任务 |\n| Haiku 3 | 快速，适合简单任务 |\n\n版本：**Claude Code 2.1.87**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":76792,"output":79,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77127,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775404740677,"responseId":"019d5e5de4c191299a577d6f11f56ed5"}}
