{"type":"message","id":"d7737f72","parentId":"a48ac411","timestamp":"2026-04-05T16:02:07.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要将 Claude Code 配置为使用 CodingPlan API（minimax-m2.5 模型），而不是默认的 Anthropic 模型。\n\n根据系统提示，有一个技能叫 `claude-code-codingplan`，可以配置 Claude Code CLI 使用 CodingPlan API。\n\n让我先读取这个技能的说明。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有专门的技能！让我帮你配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5e60b8f83fb06234bc36480cbb55","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/claude-code-codingplan/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":890,"output":106,"cacheRead":76288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775404921034,"responseId":"019d5e60a6aa037a4dd66aa5327e014c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3eb0e889","parentId":"d7737f72","timestamp":"2026-04-05T16:02:07.723Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5e60b8f83fb06234bc36480cbb55","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: claude-code-codingplan\ndescription: Configure Claude Code CLI to use CodingPlan API (compatible OpenAI format). Use when user wants to run Claude Code CLI directly with their CodingPlan API key, or when Claude Code CLI fails with authentication errors.\n---\n\n# Claude Code + CodingPlan Configuration\n\nThis skill configures the Claude Code CLI to authenticate via CodingPlan API instead of Anthropic's default API.\n\n## When to Use\n\n- User wants to run `claude` command directly in terminal\n- Claude Code CLI shows \"Authentication required\" or API errors\n- User provides CodingPlan API endpoint and key\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Collect API Credentials\n\nAsk user for:\n- **API URL**: e.g., `https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding`\n- **API Key**: The CodingPlan API key\n- **Model**: (optional) defaults to `minimax-m2.5`\n\n### 2. Create Environment File\n\nWrite to `~/.openclaw/claude.env`:\n\n```bash\n# Coding Plan API 配置\nexport ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=\"<API_KEY>\"\nexport ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"<API_URL>/v1\"\nexport ANTHROPIC_MODEL=\"minimax-m2.5\"\n```\n\n### 3. Verify Configuration\n\n```bash\nsource ~/.openclaw/claude.env && claude --print -p \"Say hi\"\n```\n\nExpected: Claude responds successfully using the specified model.\n\n## Notes\n\n- OpenClaw itself uses `openclaw.json` for API configuration—this skill is only for direct `claude` CLI usage\n- The base URL should end with `/v1` for OpenAI-compatible endpoints\n- Model name depends on what CodingPlan provider supports (common: `minimax-m2.5`)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775404927713}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa070da2","parentId":"3eb0e889","timestamp":"2026-04-05T16:02:11.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要用用户提供的信息来配置 CodingPlan API：\n- API Key: J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE\n- URL: https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding\n- 模型: minimax-m2.5\n\n让我创建 ~/.openclaw/claude.env 文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n根据技能文档配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e327b08c06f64a68b01fbc7a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > ~/.openclaw/claude.env << 'EOF'\n# Coding Plan API 配置\nexport ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=\"J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE\"\nexport ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1\"\nexport ANTHROPIC_MODEL=\"minimax-m2.5\"\nEOF\necho \"✅ 配置已写入 ~/.openclaw/claude.env\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":77763,"output":228,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775404927724,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1fa64668-58a4-4bbd-9c5a-a31d1e5bb73d"}}
