{"type":"message","id":"145020ed","parentId":"fc485c91","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:08:33.579Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_19c575dda4934405aa12e357","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 详情 ===\n{\n  \"name\": \"self-improving-agent\",\n  \"description\": \"Auto-record corrections and errors, and apply learnings\",\n  \"version\": \"3.0.10\",\n  \"entry\": \"scripts/activator.sh\",\n  \"triggers\": []\n}\n\n=== 技能描述 ===\n---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable continuous improvement. Use when: (1) A command or operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User corrects Claude ('No, that's wrong...', 'Actually...'), (3) User requests a capability that doesn't exist, (4) An external API or tool fails, (5) Claude realizes its knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6) A better approach is discovered for a recurring task. Also review learnings before major tasks.\"\nmetadata:\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":18,"aggregated":"=== 详情 ===\n{\n  \"name\": \"self-improving-agent\",\n  \"description\": \"Auto-record corrections and errors, and apply learnings\",\n  \"version\": \"3.0.10\",\n  \"entry\": \"scripts/activator.sh\",\n  \"triggers\": []\n}\n\n=== 技能描述 ===\n---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable continuous improvement. Use when: (1) A command or operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User corrects Claude ('No, that's wrong...', 'Actually...'), (3) User requests a capability that doesn't exist, (4) An external API or tool fails, (5) Claude realizes its knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6) A better approach is discovered for a recurring task. Also review learnings before major tasks.\"\nmetadata:\n---","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775412513573}}
