{"type":"message","id":"0af54021","parentId":"f60946ad","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:34:15.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问执行任务前需要做什么。根据task_orchestrator的规则，执行任务前需要先进行评分。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n执行任务前需要**评分**：\n\n```bash\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=你的任务\"\n```\n\n根据分数选择执行模式：\n\n| 分数 | 执行方式 | 超时 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 180s |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 160s |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s |\n\n这就是**任务编排系统**的流程：先评分 → 再执行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":84834,"output":160,"cacheRead":5376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90370,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775414039656,"responseId":"019d5eec51ffa93cb323bf3dd6edb425"}}
