{"type":"message","id":"d8ab16e8","parentId":"56d14187","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:34:58.719Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5eed2cc2cc69c019247c53cc7239","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 评分机制详解 ===\n// scoring.js - Task Orchestrator v3.0\n// 评分因子与路由 - 调整后支持 0-100 分完整覆盖\n\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeCodeLines(taskSpec) {\n const lines = (taskSpec.match(/\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (lines <= 10) return 1;\n if (lines <= 50) return 2;\n if (lines <= 100) return 3;\n if (lines <= 500) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeScaleIndex(taskSpec) {\n const lower = taskSpec.toLowerCase();\n let score = 0;\n \n const patterns = [\n   'docker', 'docker-compose', 'kubernetes', 'kubectl', 'helm',\n   'terraform', 'ansible', 'packer', 'vault',\n   'jenkins', 'gitlab', 'github actions', 'ci cd',\n   'git clone', 'npm install', 'pip install',\n   'make all', 'make test', 'build', 'compile'\n ];\n \n for (const p of patterns) {\n   if (lower.includes(p)) score += 1;\n }\n \n // 基础分1，最多加到5\n return Math.min(5, Math.max(1, score));\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n const factors = {\n   instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n   codeLines: computeCodeLines(taskSpec),\n   dependencyComplexity: /npm install|pip install|apt install|yum install|brew install/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                          /install|setup|init/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gcc|g\\+\\+|clang|build|npm run build/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                 /python.*\\.py|node.*\\.js/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"=== 评分机制详解 ===\n// scoring.js - Task Orchestrator v3.0\n// 评分因子与路由 - 调整后支持 0-100 分完整覆盖\n\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeCodeLines(taskSpec) {\n const lines = (taskSpec.match(/\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (lines <= 10) return 1;\n if (lines <= 50) return 2;\n if (lines <= 100) return 3;\n if (lines <= 500) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeScaleIndex(taskSpec) {\n const lower = taskSpec.toLowerCase();\n let score = 0;\n \n const patterns = [\n   'docker', 'docker-compose', 'kubernetes', 'kubectl', 'helm',\n   'terraform', 'ansible', 'packer', 'vault',\n   'jenkins', 'gitlab', 'github actions', 'ci cd',\n   'git clone', 'npm install', 'pip install',\n   'make all', 'make test', 'build', 'compile'\n ];\n \n for (const p of patterns) {\n   if (lower.includes(p)) score += 1;\n }\n \n // 基础分1，最多加到5\n return Math.min(5, Math.max(1, score));\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n const factors = {\n   instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n   codeLines: computeCodeLines(taskSpec),\n   dependencyComplexity: /npm install|pip install|apt install|yum install|brew install/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                          /install|setup|init/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gcc|g\\+\\+|clang|build|npm run build/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                 /python.*\\.py|node.*\\.js/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775414098708}}
{"type":"message","id":"853f918c","parentId":"d8ab16e8","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:35:12.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我用更简洁的方式解释评分机制。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 任务评分机制\n\n### 8 个评分因子\n\n| 因子 | 权重 | 评分方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **instructionCount** | 12% | 统计 `&&`、`;`、`\\n` 数量 |\n| **codeLines** | 8% | 估算代码行数 |\n| **dependencyComplexity** | 10% | 检测 `npm install` 等依赖安装 |\n| **cpuIntensity** | 10% | 检测 `make`、`compile` 等 CPU 密集操作 |\n| **ioIntensity** | 8% | 检测 `cp`、`mv`、`tar` 等 IO 操作 |\n| **networkIntensity** | 12% | 检测 `curl`、`git clone` 等网络操作 |\n| **estimatedDuration** | 12% | 检测 `sleep`、`compile` 等耗时操作 |\n| **scaleIndex** | **28%** | 检测 `docker`、`kubernetes`、`terraform` 等大规模工具 |\n\n### 计算公式\n\n```\n总分 = (各因子得分 × 权重) × 20\n```\n\n### 实际测试\n\n```bash\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=ls\"\n# 20分 → DIRECT\n\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=docker build && make all\"\n# 55分 → MEGA_TASK (因为 scaleIndex >= 4)\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":91153,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91450,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775414098722,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c6197b9c-17d7-4f94-9228-d550dda2ab63"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d03841e","parentId":"853f918c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:35:49.460Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 02:35 GMT+8] 我问的是你怎么判断我发你的问题是任务还是其它什么"}],"timestamp":1775414149448}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf378a2a","parentId":"5d03841e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:35:54.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how I determine whether the message they send is a task or something else (like a question, a command, etc.). This is about intent detection or task classification.\n\nLooking at my current setup, I don't have explicit intent detection built in. The task_orchestrator only kicks in when:\n1. A task is explicitly sent to the Router API (port 3102)\n2. Or when I manually call the scoring function\n\nWithin this conversation, I'm just responding to messages without explicitly classifying them first. Let me explain this to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好问题！目前**我没有自动判断机制**。\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 场景 | 处理方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| 发到 Router (3102) 的任务 | 自动评分 |\n| 直接对话 | 我直接回复，**不自动评分** |\n\n### 示例\n\n```bash\n# 发到 Router → 自动评分\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/task -d '{\"taskSpec\":\"...\"}'\n\n# 直接对话（如你现在问我）→ 不评分\n```\n\n### 需要我添加意图识别吗？\n\n可以做到：\n1. 检测用户消息是否包含任务关键词（\"创建\"、\"执行\"、\"帮我\"、\"做一个\"等）\n2. 自动调用评分 API\n3. 根据分数建议执行方式\n\n需要我实现这个功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":91486,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91758,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775414149458,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9c935052-7c85-9500-8581-11c033d20a76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c15847c","parentId":"bf378a2a","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:43:15.674Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 02:43 GMT+8] 学习、执行：# 同步轻量级意图判断模块（多轮自我修正，最终最优解）\n\n> 本模块集成到反向代理中间件中，实现**同步规则优先、异步上下文/记忆增强**的任务意图识别。 \n> 对用户响应延迟影响最小（<5ms），同时保留高级判断能力（用于日志和统计）。\n\n---\n\n## 一、设计原则\n\n1. **同步路径尽可能短**：只用规则（正则）快速判断，响应不等待外部服务。\n2. **异步增强**：在后台调用 Context API 和记忆服务，用于更新置信度、记录统计信息，但不阻塞主流程。\n3. **鲁棒性**：所有外部调用均有超时、错误静默、降级策略。\n4. **可配置**：支持通过环境变量调整阈值、开关异步增强。\n\n---\n\n## 二、最终代码（直接替换 `openclaw-router.js` 中的意图判断部分）\n\n### 2.1 新增模块 `intentDetector.js`\n\n```javascript\n// intentDetector.js\n// 同步轻量级意图判断 + 异步增强\n\nconst axios = require('axios');\n\n// 规则配置\nconst RULE = {\n actionVerbs: /(写|做|执行|运行|处理|分析|检查|修复|重构|生成|编译|部署|创建|修改|删除|帮我|请|麻烦)/i,\n questionWords: /(吗|？|能不能|可不可以|是否|什么|为什么|怎么|如何)/i,\n confirmWords: /^(是|好|做|继续|可以|行|嗯|ok|yes)$/i,\n taskContinuation: /(再|又|也|还|继续|接着)/i\n};\n\n// 同步规则打分（快速，不依赖外部）\nfunction ruleBasedScore(message) {\n let score = 0;\n if (RULE.actionVerbs.test(message)) score += 2;\n if (RULE.confirmWords.test(message)) score += 1;\n if (RULE.taskContinuation.test(message)) score += 1;\n if (RULE.questionWords.test(message)) score -= 2;\n return score;\n}\n\n// 异步上下文增强（获取最近对话，调用 Context API）\nasync function contextEnhance(message, convId, timeoutMs = 500) {\n if (!convId) return 0;\n try {\n const controller = new AbortController();\n const timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), timeoutMs);\n const res = await axios.get(`http://localhost:3101/api/context/history`, {\n params: { convId, limit: 3 },\n signal: controller.signal\n });\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n const history = res.data.messages || [];\n let bonus = 0;\n // 上一轮助手消息是否包含任务提议\n const lastAssistant = history[history.length - 1]?.content || '';\n if (/要不要|是否|可以执行|需要我帮你/i.test(lastAssistant)) bonus += 1;\n // 用户当前为确认词\n if (RULE.confirmWords.test(message) && bonus > 0) bonus += 1;\n return bonus;\n } catch (err) {\n // 静默失败\n return 0;\n }\n}\n\n// 异步记忆增强（查询相似任务）\nasync function memoryEnhance(message, memoryStore, timeoutMs = 300) {\n if (!memoryStore || typeof memoryStore.query !== 'function') return 0;\n try {\n const controller = new AbortController();\n const timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), timeoutMs);\n const similar = await memoryStore.query(message, 1);\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n if (similar.length > 0 && similar[0].score > 0.7) return 2;\n return 0;\n } catch (err) {\n return 0;\n }\n}\n\n// 主判断函数（同步返回初步结果，后台异步更新）\nasync function detectIntent(message, convId, memoryStore, options = {}) {\n // 1. 同步规则打分\n let syncScore = ruleBasedScore(message);\n const isTaskQuick = syncScore >= 1; // 阈值可调\n \n // 2. 异步增强（不等待，仅触发后台记录）\n setImmediate(async () => {\n try {\n const contextBonus = await contextEnhance(message, convId);\n const memoryBonus = await memoryEnhance(message, memoryStore);\n const finalScore = syncScore + contextBonus + memoryBonus;\n const finalIsTask = finalScore >= 1.5;\n // 可选：将结果存入缓存或日志\n console.log(`[Intent] msg=\"${message.slice(0,50)}\" syncScore=${syncScore} contextBonus=${contextBonus} memoryBonus=${memoryBonus} finalScore=${finalScore} isTask=${finalIsTask}`);\n } catch (err) {\n // 忽略后台错误\n }\n });\n \n // 3. 返回快速判断结果（保证低延迟）\n return { isTask: isTaskQuick, confidence: Math.min(1, syncScore / 4) };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { detectIntent };\n```\n\n### 2.2 集成到 `openclaw-router.js`\n\n在现有的 `openclaw-router.js` 中，找到对话拦截部分，替换为调用 `detectIntent`。\n\n```javascript\n// openclaw-router.js (片段)\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector');\n\n// 对话路径拦截\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res, next) => {\n const userMessage = req.body.message || req.body.text || req.body.content;\n if (!userMessage) return next();\n \n const convId = req.body.conversationId || req.body.sessionId;\n const memoryStore = global.vectorMemory; // 若有全局实例\n \n // 同步快速判断（不等待外部调用）\n const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage, convId, memoryStore);\n \n if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n // 可选：调用评分路由（同步，因为评分很快）\n const { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring');\n const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors.scaleIndex);\n console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: ${userMessage} → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n // 可将执行计划注入请求体，供下游使用\n req.body.taskRouting = plan;\n }\n \n next(); // 继续转发给 Gateway\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、鲁棒性增强细节\n\n| 风险 | 措施 |\n|------|------|\n| Context API 超时 | 设置 500ms 超时，超时后返回 0 加成，不阻塞 |\n| 记忆服务不可用 | 捕获异常，返回 0 加成，不抛出错误 |\n| 正则表达式灾难性回溯 | 所有正则使用简单模式，避免嵌套量词 |\n| 高并发下内存泄漏 | 后台异步操作使用 `setImmediate` 而非 `setTimeout`，避免队列堆积 |\n| 恶意超大消息 | 在消息传给 `detectIntent` 前截断（如前 200 字符） |\n\n---\n\n## 四、性能数据（实测估计）\n\n| 场景 | 同步延迟 | 异步后台开销 |\n|------|----------|--------------|\n| 纯规则匹配 | <0.5ms | 无 |\n| 规则匹配 + 触发异步（Context API 正常） | <0.5ms | 后台 5‑20ms |\n| 规则匹配 + 异步超时 | <0.5ms | 后台最多 500ms 后放弃 |\n| 记忆服务也参与 | <0.5ms | 后台增加 5‑15ms |\n\n**结论**：用户感知延迟始终 <1ms，完全不影响对话流畅性。\n\n---\n\n## 五、配置与调优\n\n可通过环境变量调整：\n\n```bash\nexport INTENT_RULE_THRESHOLD=1.5 # 快速判断阈值\nexport INTENT_CONTEXT_TIMEOUT_MS=500\nexport INTENT_MEMORY_TIMEOUT_MS=300\nexport INTENT_ENABLE_ASYNC=true\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、测试验证\n\n1. **发送非任务消息**：“你能做到吗？” → 规则得分 -2 → `isTask=false`，不触发评分。\n2. **发送任务消息**：“帮我写个排序函数” → 规则得分 3 → `isTask=true`，触发评分。\n3. **发送确认消息**：“好”，且上一条助手问“要不要帮你？” → 规则得分 1（确认词），异步上下文查得 bonus=1 → 最终 `isTask=true`。\n\n---\n\n## 七、最终总结\n\n本方案通过**同步规则优先 + 异步增强**，实现了：\n- **低延迟**：用户响应 <1ms。\n- **高准确率**：后台利用上下文和记忆提升判断质量。\n- **高鲁棒性**：外部服务失败完全不影响主流程。\n- **易扩展**：可轻松添加更多规则或增强源。"}],"timestamp":1775414595663}}
