{"type":"message","id":"59cf7a3d","parentId":"0f3008d8","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:44:46.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"意图判断模块已经生效！测试结果正确：- \"帮我写一个排序函数\" → isTask: true (动作词 \"写\")\n- \"你能做到吗？\" → isTask: false (疑问词 \"吗\")\n- \"好\" → isTask: true (确认词)\n- \"接着执行\" → isTask: true (任务继续词)\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 检查通过\n\n| 测试 | 消息 | 结果 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 任务 | \"帮我写一个排序函数\" | ✅ isTask=true, confidence=0.5 |\n| 询问 | \"你能做到吗？\" | ✅ isTask=false, confidence=0 |\n| 确认 | \"好\" | ✅ isTask=true, confidence=0.25 |\n| 继续 | \"接着执行\" | ✅ isTask=true, confidence=0.75 |\n\n**意图判断模块生效中！** 🎉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":96685,"output":187,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775414669593,"responseId":"019d5ef54e0e2959432fc6df49ab6fab"}}
