{"type":"message","id":"1a70aca9","parentId":"be331e00","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:45:40.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what needs to be done before executing a task. Based on the system we've built, the workflow is:\n\n1. Intent Detection - determine if the user's message is a task\n2. Task Scoring - calculate the complexity score\n3. Choose execution mode based on score\n\nLet me explain this concisely.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 任务执行流程\n\n```\n用户消息 → 意图判断 → 评分 → 选择执行模式 → 执行\n```\n\n**每次执行任务前：**\n\n| 步骤 | 操作 | API |\n|------|------|-----|\n| 1 | 意图判断 | `POST /api/intent` |\n| 2 | 任务评分 | `GET /api/score` |\n| 3 | 获取执行计划 | 返回 mode + 超时 + 内存 |\n\n**示例：**\n```bash\n# 1. 判断是否是任务\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/intent -d '{\"message\":\"帮我写个函数\"}'\n# → isTask=true\n\n# 2. 评分\ncurl \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=帮我写个函数\"\n# → score=20, mode=DIRECT\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":7337,"output":244,"cacheRead":89728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775414727292,"responseId":"019d5ef6cdb100dfc09520a3257c0fa5"}}
