{"type":"message","id":"56bf0e7f","parentId":"6233b8b3","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:55:47.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个 React 前端应用，使用了 Lit 框架。很难直接从前端代码中提取 API 端点。\n\n从配置文件中，我看到 Gateway 使用了 `mode: \"local\"` 和 token 认证。\n\n让我换一种方法 - 直接检查 Gateway 配置文件或者查看实际的请求日志，看看对话请求是怎么发送的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5f00238bd469f106c27de85d3f4b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 探索 Gateway API 端点 ===\" \n\necho \"【尝试常见 API 端点】\"\nfor path in \"/api\" \"/v1\" \"/api/v1\" \"/chat\" \"/api/chat\" \"/api/messages\" \"/send\" \"/api/send\" \"/prompt\" \"/api/prompt\"; do\n  result=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://127.0.0.1:18789$path 2>/dev/null)\n  if [ \"$result\" != \"404\" ]; then\n    echo \"$path: $result\"\n  fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【检查配置中是否有 API 信息】\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.json | grep -i \"api\\|endpoint\\|url\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":118195,"output":255,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132786,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775415321109,"responseId":"019d5effdf9aaf83a7d46b3f9f28a4c9"}}
