{"type":"message","id":"b7d760b4","parentId":"10c350cc","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:56:13.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！Gateway 支持以下端点：\n- `/v1` - 200\n- `/chat` - 200\n- `/send` - 200\n- `/prompt` - 200\n\n让我测试一下这些端点，找到发送消息的正确路径：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d5f00818d1a0d56cbedfb684a48a4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 测试 Gateway 聊天端点 ===\" \n\necho \"【1】POST /chat\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"hello\"}' | head -c 200\n\necho \"\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【2】POST /send\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"hello\"}' | head -c 200\n\necho \"\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【3】POST /prompt\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/prompt \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"hello\"}' | head -c 200"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":118299,"output":266,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775415347359,"responseId":"019d5f0040ba085b84bd5462c86add33"}}
