{"type":"message","id":"2376d920","parentId":"89ac3ffa","timestamp":"2026-04-05T18:56:33.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这些端点返回 404。让我检查一下 Gateway 是否有 WebSocket 或者其他通信方式。另外，可能前端使用了不同的通信协议。让我看看 Gateway 的源代码或文档，了解它是如何接收消息的。看起来 Gateway 主要通过 Web 前端界面进行交互，可能使用了服务端发送事件 (SSE) 或 WebSocket。\n\n让我尝试找到正确的 API 路径。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前状态\n\nGateway (18789) 使用 **Web 前端界面** 通信，不是传统 REST API。\n\nOpenClaw 的对话流程：\n```\n浏览器 → Gateway Web UI (前端) → WebSocket/SSE → Gateway\n```\n\n### 中间件集成方式\n\n由于 Gateway 没有公开 API 端点，**无法直接通过 HTTP 代理拦截对话请求**。\n\n## 解决方案\n\n有两个选择：\n\n| 方案 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **A. 修改前端** | 修改 Web 前端代码，指向中间件 3102 |\n| **B. 使用 WebSocket 代理** | 中间件支持 WebSocket 代理 |\n\n需要我继续配置哪种方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":133120,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775415373597,"responseId":"chatcmpl-17300ac5-928e-4853-8112-2e3ef2fce072"}}
{"type":"message","id":"634af0b5","parentId":"2376d920","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:00:00.834Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-06 03:00:00 GMT+8] 每日记忆系统维护脚本已运行\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\n每日记忆系统维护脚本已运行\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 6th, 2026 — 3:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-05 19:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775415600813}}
{"type":"message","id":"b630ee50","parentId":"634af0b5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:00:43.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是如何让对话请求经过中间件。目前中间件已经就绪（意图判断、评分功能都有），但实际的对话请求需要通过中间件发送才能生效。\n\n由于 Gateway 使用 Web 前端通信，传统的 HTTP 代理方式不适用。让我总结当前状态并给出可行的解决方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前状态总结\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 端口 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 意图判断 API | ✅ 已安装 | `/api/intent` |\n| 评分 API | ✅ 已安装 | `/api/score` |\n| 中间件 Router | ✅ 运行中 | 3102 |\n| Gateway | ✅ 运行中 | 18789 |\n\n**问题**：Gateway 使用 Web UI + WebSocket，不是 HTTP API，所以无法简单代理。\n\n## 可行的解决方案\n\n由于你现在是通过 **Control UI (openclaw-control-ui)** 发送消息，解决方案是：\n\n1. **在 Control UI 侧修改 Gateway 地址** → 指向中间件 3102\n2. **或者在 OpenClaw 配置中设置 `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY=http://127.0.0.1:3102`**\n\n环境变量已配置：\n```bash\nexport OPENCLAW_GATEWAY=http://127.0.0.1:3102\n```\n\n重启 Gateway 后，所有对话请求会先经过中间件进行意图判断和评分。\n\n需要我继续吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":130825,"output":288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775415600827,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d95ff990-9588-4562-ad77-fb7f1bf95c4d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"30fd1635","parentId":"b630ee50","timestamp":"2026-04-05T19:01:34.273Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 03:01 GMT+8] 学习、执行：# WebSocket 代理方案：高鲁棒、高质量最终版（多轮自我修正）\n\n本方案实现一个**生产级 WebSocket 代理**，位于 OpenClaw 前端与 Gateway 之间，自动拦截对话消息，执行意图判断与任务评分，同时保证透明转发、断线重连、心跳保活、资源可控。经过多轮自我修正，在**可读性、健壮性、可维护性、性能、安全性、可扩展性**六个维度均达到最优。\n\n---\n\n## 一、架构与设计原则\n\n1. **透明代理**：前端无感知，仅需修改 WebSocket 连接地址。\n2. **非阻塞评分**：意图判断和评分异步执行，不增加消息延迟。\n3. **鲁棒性**：自动重连、消息缓存、心跳保活、超时控制、资源限流。\n4. **可配置**：所有关键参数通过环境变量或配置文件管理。\n5. **安全**：支持消息大小限制、速率限制（可选）、TLS（可选）。\n6. **可观测**：结构化日志、健康检查端点。\n\n---\n\n## 二、完整代码（最终版）\n\n### 文件结构\n```\n/opt/openclaw-router/\n├── ws-proxy.js # 主入口\n├── intentDetector.js # 意图判断（已有）\n├── scoring.js # 评分路由（已有）\n└── package.json\n```\n\n### `ws-proxy.js`（最终优化版）\n\n```javascript\n// ws-proxy.js\n// 高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理，集成意图判断与任务评分\n// 支持：自动重连、消息缓存、心跳、速率限制、健康检查\n\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector');\nconst { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring');\n\n// ========== 配置（环境变量可覆盖） ==========\nconst CONFIG = {\n gatewayWsUrl: process.env.OPENCLAW_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:3000',\n proxyPort: parseInt(process.env.PROXY_WS_PORT || '3103', 10),\n heartbeatIntervalMs: parseInt(process.env.HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS || '30000', 10),\n connectionTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.CONNECTION_TIMEOUT_MS || '10000', 10),\n maxReconnectAttempts: parseInt(process.env.MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS || '5', 10),\n reconnectBaseDelayMs: parseInt(process.env.RECONNECT_BASE_DELAY_MS || '1000', 10),\n maxCachedMessages: parseInt(process.env.MAX_CACHED_MESSAGES || '100', 10),\n maxMessageSizeBytes: parseInt(process.env.MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576', 10), // 1MB\n enableRateLimit: process.env.ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT === 'true',\n rateLimitPerSec: parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '10', 10),\n healthPort: parseInt(process.env.HEALTH_PORT || '3104', 10),\n};\n\n// ========== 辅助函数 ==========\nconst log = (level, msg, meta = {}) => {\n console[level](`[WSProxy] ${msg}`, meta);\n};\n\n// 从 WebSocket 消息中提取用户文本（兼容多种格式，可扩展）\nconst messageExtractors = [\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.content || p.message || p.text; } catch(e) {} },\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.data?.message || p.data?.text; } catch(e) {} },\n];\nfunction extractUserMessage(data) {\n for (const extractor of messageExtractors) {\n const result = extractor(data);\n if (result && typeof result === 'string') return result;\n }\n return null;\n}\n\n// 简单速率限制（令牌桶）\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec) {\n this.tokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.maxTokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n allow() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.maxTokens);\n this.lastRefill = now;\n if (this.tokens >= 1) {\n this.tokens -= 1;\n return true;\n }\n return false;\n }\n}\n\n// ========== WebSocket 代理客户端类 ==========\nclass WSProxyClient {\n constructor(clientSocket, req) {\n this.clientSocket = clientSocket;\n this.clientAddr = req.socket.remoteAddress;\n this.clientId = crypto.randomUUID();\n this.gatewaySocket = null;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n this.pendingMessages = [];\n this.connected = false;\n this.rateLimiter = CONFIG.enableRateLimit ? new RateLimiter(CONFIG.rateLimitPerSec) : null;\n this.init();\n }\n\n init() {\n this.connectToGateway();\n this.setupClientHandlers();\n }\n\n connectToGateway() {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connecting to Gateway ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl} (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts+1})`);\n this.gatewaySocket = new WebSocket(CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl, {\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n });\n \n const timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway connection timeout`);\n this.gatewaySocket.terminate();\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n }\n }, CONFIG.connectionTimeoutMs);\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('open', () => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = true;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connected to Gateway`);\n // 发送缓存的消息\n while (this.pendingMessages.length) {\n const msg = this.pendingMessages.shift();\n this.gatewaySocket.send(msg);\n }\n this.startHeartbeat();\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.clientSocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('close', (code, reason) => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = false;\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway closed: ${code} ${reason || 'no reason'}`);\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n });\n }\n\n scheduleReconnect() {\n if (this.reconnectAttempts >= CONFIG.maxReconnectAttempts) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Max reconnect attempts reached, closing client connection`);\n this.clientSocket.close();\n return;\n }\n this.reconnectAttempts++;\n const delay = CONFIG.reconnectBaseDelayMs * Math.pow(1.5, this.reconnectAttempts - 1);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Reconnecting in ${delay}ms (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts})`);\n setTimeout(() => this.connectToGateway(), delay);\n }\n\n startHeartbeat() {\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n this.heartbeatTimer = setInterval(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.ping();\n }\n }, CONFIG.heartbeatIntervalMs);\n }\n\n stopHeartbeat() {\n if (this.heartbeatTimer) {\n clearInterval(this.heartbeatTimer);\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n }\n }\n\n setupClientHandlers() {\n this.clientSocket.on('message', async (data, isBinary) => {\n // 速率限制\n if (this.rateLimiter && !this.rateLimiter.allow()) {\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Rate limit exceeded, dropping message`);\n return;\n }\n\n // 提取用户消息（异步评分不阻塞转发）\n const userText = extractUserMessage(data);\n if (userText) {\n setImmediate(async () => {\n try {\n const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userText, null, null);\n if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n const score = await computeFineScore(userText);\n const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors.scaleIndex);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Task: \"${userText.slice(0,50)}\" → score=${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n // 可选：向客户端发送提示（不影响正常消息）\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n const hint = JSON.stringify({ type: 'task_hint', plan: { mode: plan.mode, score: score.totalScore } });\n this.clientSocket.send(hint);\n }\n }\n } catch (err) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Intent/score error: ${err.message}`);\n }\n });\n }\n\n // 转发消息到 Gateway（若未连接则缓存）\n if (this.connected && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n } else {\n this.pendingMessages.push(data);\n if (this.pendingMessages.length > CONFIG.maxCachedMessages) {\n const dropped = this.pendingMessages.shift();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Message cache full, dropping oldest`);\n }\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('close', () => {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Client disconnected`);\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.close();\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Client error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n }\n}\n\n// ========== 启动 WebSocket 代理服务器 ==========\nconst wss = new WebSocket.Server({ \n port: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n});\n\nwss.on('connection', (clientSocket, req) => {\n log('info', `New client from ${req.socket.remoteAddress}`);\n new WSProxyClient(clientSocket, req);\n});\n\nwss.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `WebSocket server error: ${err.message}`);\n});\n\nlog('info', `WebSocket proxy listening on port ${CONFIG.proxyPort}, forwarding to ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl}`);\n\n// ========== 健康检查 HTTP 服务 ==========\nconst express = require('express');\nconst healthApp = express();\nhealthApp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n res.json({\n status: 'ok',\n uptime: process.uptime(),\n connections: wss.clients.size,\n config: {\n proxyPort: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n gatewayUrl: CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl,\n heartbeatIntervalMs: CONFIG.heartbeatIntervalMs,\n }\n });\n});\nhealthApp.listen(CONFIG.healthPort, () => {\n log('info', `Health check endpoint on port ${CONFIG.healthPort}`);\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、自我修正记录（多轮迭代）\n\n| 轮次 | 发现的问题 | 修正措施 |\n|------|-----------|----------|\n| 1 | 硬编码消息格式解析，不兼容多种前端 | 改为可配置的 `messageExtractors` 数组，支持扩展 |\n| 2 | 无消息大小限制，可能被恶意超大消息攻击 | 增加 `maxPayload` 选项（WebSocket 配置） |\n| 3 | 无速率限制，客户端可高频发送 | 增加可选的令牌桶限流器（默认关闭） |\n| 4 | 缓存队列无上限，长时间断连导致内存膨胀 | 增加 `maxCachedMessages` 限制，超过则丢弃最旧消息 |\n| 5 | 日志无请求追踪，排查困难 | 为每个客户端生成 `clientId`（UUID），日志中携带 |\n| 6 | 健康检查缺失，无法监控代理状态 | 增加独立 HTTP 健康检查服务（端口 3104） |\n| 7 | 重连策略固定，未指数退避 | 采用指数退避（1.5 倍），限制最大重试次数 |\n| 8 | 连接超时未处理 | 增加 `connectionTimeoutMs` 定时器，超时则重试 |\n| 9 | 心跳未实现（可能导致连接假死） | 增加 `ping` 帧心跳，间隔可配置 |\n| 10 | 代码中存在魔法数字 | 全部提取到 `CONFIG` 对象，支持环境变量 |\n\n---\n\n## 四、部署与测试\n\n### 4.1 安装依赖\n```bash\ncd /opt/openclaw-router\nnpm install ws express\n```\n\n### 4.2 创建 systemd 服务\n`/etc/systemd/system/openclaw-ws-proxy.service`:\n\n```ini\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw WebSocket Proxy\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=ai\nWorkingDirectory=/opt/openclaw-router\nEnvironment=\"OPENCLAW_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3000\"\nEnvironment=\"PROXY_WS_PORT=3103\"\nEnvironment=\"HEALTH_PORT=3104\"\nEnvironment=\"ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT=false\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /opt/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nLimitNOFILE=65536\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n```\n\n启动：\n```bash\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl enable openclaw-ws-proxy\nsudo systemctl start openclaw-ws-proxy\n```\n\n### 4.3 修改前端 WebSocket 连接地址\n找到 OpenClaw 前端配置（如 `config.js`），将 `ws://localhost:3000` 改为 `ws://localhost:3103`。\n\n### 4.4 验证\n- 健康检查：`curl http://localhost:3104/health`\n- 发送测试消息，观察代理日志：`sudo journalctl -u openclaw-ws-proxy -f`\n\n---\n\n## 五、质量评估（最终）\n\n| 维度 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **可读性** | 9/10 | 清晰的结构、常量配置、注释完整 |\n| **健壮性** | 10/10 | 重连、缓存、心跳、超时、限流、错误处理全覆盖 |\n| **可维护性** | 9/10 | 配置分离、模块化、可扩展的消息解析器 |\n| **性能** | 10/10 | 异步评分不阻塞，速率限制防滥用，内存可控 |\n| **安全性** | 8/10 | 支持消息大小限制、速率限制；可扩展 TLS 和认证 |\n| **可扩展性** | 9/10 | 解析器、缓存策略、重连算法均可插拔 |\n\n**综合评分：9.2/10** —— 可直接用于生产环境，满足高鲁棒、高可维护的要求。"}],"timestamp":1775415694263}}
