{"type":"message","id":"e428e6e3","parentId":"390df1c8","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:32:14.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！Gateway 端口配置在 `channel-DjAoNe_R.js` 中：`const port = typeof cfg?.gateway?.port === \"number\" ? cfg.gateway.port : 18789;`\n\n这意味着 Gateway 的端口是从配置文件 `cfg.gateway.port` 读取的，如果没配置默认是 18789。\n\n让我检查 OpenClaw 的配置文件是否有这个选项。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d60d86252f3d29ce974bdd27e53c0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"【查找 Gateway 配置来源】\"\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\n\necho \"搜索配置文件中的 gateway.port...\"\ngrep -r \"gateway\" ~/.openclaw/*.json ~/.openclaw/*.yaml 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"vector\\|memory\" | head -10\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【检查 config 加载位置】\"\ngrep -r \"gateway.*port\" /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/*.js 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3772,"output":213,"cacheRead":83328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775446322138,"responseId":"019d60d848dd3151795560d82e5a6a81"}}
