_KIND=gateway\\nCONTEXT_API_PORT=3101\\nROUTER_PORT=3102\\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\\nOPENCLAW_SYSTEMD_UNIT=openclaw-gateway.service\\nOPENCLAW_WINDOWS_TASK_NAME=OpenClaw Gateway\\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY=http://127.0.0.1:18789\\n\\n【Gateway 监听的实际端口仍然是 18789】\\n可能原因: systemd 服务有端口参数覆盖，或 Gateway 启动参数覆盖\",\"cwd\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775446867050}}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775446877920}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0fc0cc9","parentId":"03a4de0f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:41:24.177Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789` 是在 Gateway 运行时动态设置的环境变量，不是预先配置在 .bashrc 中的。这个环境变量是由 Gateway 启动时自己设置的。\n\n关键问题是 Gateway 启动时带有 `--port 18789` 参数。看日志：\n```\nCommand: /usr/bin/node ... gateway --port 18789\n```\n\n这个 `--port 18789` 可能是 systemd 服务文件中硬编码的参数。让我检查一下 systemd 服务文件的内容。\n\n由于我没有 sudo 权限，无法检查系统级的 systemd 服务文件。但问题很明确：\n- Gateway 的启动命令带有 `--port 18789` 参数\n- 这覆盖了配置文件中的 `port: 3103`\n\n用户需要修改 systemd 服务文件中的启动参数，或者直接修改配置文件后确保 Gateway 重新读取配置。\n\n让我告诉用户这个情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 原因已找到\n\nGateway 启动时带有 `--port 18789` 硬编码参数，覆盖了配置文件：\n\n```\nCommand: /usr/bin/node ... gateway --port 18789\n```\n\n**解决方案：** 需要修改 systemd 服务文件中的启动参数。\n\n由于我没有 sudo 权限，请手动执行：\n\n```bash\n# 查看当前服务文件\nsudo systemctl cat openclaw-gateway\n\n# 找到 --port 参数，修改为 --port 3103\n\n# 或者直接修改\nsudo sed -i 's/--port 18789/--port 3103/g' /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 重载并重启\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-gateway\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":101228,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101551,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775446877935,"responseId":"chatcmpl-367796c0-b398-461e-92ae-f427ec65d227"}}
