{"type":"message","id":"71ed9f87","parentId":"5ca19040","timestamp":"2026-04-06T03:59:46.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"原来 Gateway 根本没有 systemd 服务文件，它是直接运行的进程。这就是为什么它一直用 18789 端口。我们需要找到 Gateway 是如何启动的，然后修改它的启动方式。\n\n让我检查一下 Gateway 是怎么启动的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_06cfe4aeefd44a0db7eea367","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 查找 Gateway 启动方式 ===\" \necho \"\"\n\necho \"【1. 检查 openclaw 命令如何启动 gateway】\"\nwhich openclaw\necho \"\"\necho \"【2. 查找启动脚本】\"\nps aux | grep openclaw | grep -v grep\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【3. 检查启动命令】\"\ncat /proc/$(pgrep -f \"openclaw-gateway\" | head -1)/cmdline | tr '\\0' ' '\necho \"\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":102132,"output":168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775447983347,"responseId":"chatcmpl-485c29d7-23b0-4c55-a0af-ce2c6efc6108"}}
