{"type":"message","id":"c6ac7343","parentId":"5aaa016f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:00:26.424Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0a9928caf9db42a4b3ba388d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 user systemd 服务文件 ===\n\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\nAfter=network-online.target\nWants=network-online.target\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=30\nTimeoutStartSec=30\nSuccessExitStatus=0 143\nKillMode=control-group\nEnvironment=HOME=/home/ai\nEnvironment=TMPDIR=/tmp\nEnvironment=PATH=/home/ai/.nvm/current/bin:/home/ai/.local/bin:/home/ai/.npm-global/bin:/home/ai/bin:/home/ai/.volta/bin:/home/ai/.asdf/shims:/home/ai/.bun/bin:/home/ai/.fnm/current/bin:/home/ai/.local/share/pnpm:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_SYSTEMD_UNIT=openclaw-gateway.service\nEnvironment=\"OPENCLAW_WINDOWS_TASK_NAME=OpenClaw Gateway\"\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_SERVICE_MARKER=openclaw\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_SERVICE_KIND=gateway\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_SERVICE_VERSION=2026.3.13\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"=== 检查 user systemd 服务文件 ===\n\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\nAfter=network-online.target\nWants=network-online.target\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=30\nTimeoutStartSec=30\nSuccessExitStatus=0 143\nKillMode=control-group\nEnvironment=HOME=/home/ai\nEnvironment=TMPDIR=/tmp\nEnvironment=PATH=/home/ai/.nvm/current/bin:/home/ai/.local/bin:/home/ai/.npm-global/bin:/home/ai/bin:/home/ai/.volta/bin:/home/ai/.asdf/shims:/home/ai/.bun/bin:/home/ai/.fnm/current/bin:/home/ai/.local/share/pnpm:/usr/local/bi