{"type":"message","id":"0532b562","parentId":"959da11b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:23:49.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User is asking if WebSocket proxy on a different port can work. Let me answer their question first - yes, WebSocket proxy on a different port can work for intent detection and scoring. Then they want to know if that approach can achieve the goal.\n\nLet me re-read their question:\n\"不要websocket代理也可以做到意图判断和评分吗\"\n\nThey're asking: \"Can we do intent detection and scoring without WebSocket proxy?\"\n\nAnd now they're asking: \"Can't we just use a different port for WebSocket proxy?\"\n\nLet me answer both:\n1. Yes, without WebSocket proxy, you CAN still do intent detection and scoring - but you need to manually call the HTTP APIs (3102)\n2. Yes, we can use a different port for WebSocket proxy - just need to change the port in both the ws-proxy.js config and the frontend configuration\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n先回答你的问题：**可以！**\n\n不用 WebSocket 代理也可以做到意图判断和评分，通过 **HTTP API** (3102) 手动调用即可。\n\n---\n\n**WebSocket 换端口：可以！**\n\n把 WebSocket 代理改到 **3105** 端口：\n\n1. 修改 ws-proxy.js 和服务文件 → 端口 3105\n2. 修改前端配置 → 连接到 **3105** 而不是 **3103**\n\n这样架构就是：\n```\n前端 → 3105 (WebSocket代理+意图判断+评分) → 3103 (Gateway)\n```\n\n要做这个修改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3316,"output":299,"cacheRead":107264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775449405301,"responseId":"019d6107f3a969aac5d42d148f4a9b57"}}
{"type":"message","id":"455625f1","parentId":"0532b562","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:24:28.352Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 12:24 GMT+8] 先检查一下这样做可以吗？不要开始行动，先检查可行性进行分析判断"}],"timestamp":1775449468340}}
{"type":"message","id":"789bc206","parentId":"455625f1","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:24:36.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要我先分析可行性，不要立即行动。让我分析一下把 WebSocket 代理改到 3105 端口是否可行。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## WebSocket 代理改到 3105 端口 - 可行性分析\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 端口 | 用途 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3101 | Context API | ✅ 正常 |\n| 3102 | HTTP Router (意图判断+评分) | ✅ 正常 |\n| 3103 | Gateway | ✅ 正常 |\n| 3104 | 健康检查 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 3105 | 未使用 | 可用 ✅ |\n\n### 需要修改的内容\n\n| 文件 | 修改项 |\n|------|--------|\n| `ws-proxy.js` | `PROXY_WS_PORT` → 3105 |\n| `openclaw-ws-proxy.service` | `PROXY_WS_PORT=3105` |\n| `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` | `gateway.port` → 3105 |\n| Gateway 服务文件 | 改回 `--port 3105` |\n\n### 潜在问题\n\n1. **Gateway 已在 3103**：需要把 Gateway 改到 3105（刚改过，可能需要再改）\n2. **前端配置**：需要让前端连接 3105\n3. **配置复杂度**：端口变来变去，可能混淆\n\n### 结论\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 端口可用 | ✅ 3105 空闲 |\n| 技术可行 | ✅ 完全可行 |\n| 复杂度 | ⚠️ 需要改 4 处 |\n| 建议 | ✅ 可行，但目前 HTTP API 已可用 |\n\n**建议**：先用 HTTP API (3102) 手动调用即可，WebSocket 代理不是必须的。等需要实时意图判断时再改。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":110984,"output":377,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111361,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775449468350,"responseId":"chatcmpl-63c7b795-190a-4454-900f-6e6e90e101e9"}}
