{"type":"message","id":"f16a8b97","parentId":"2844a21c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:26:29.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a plan/proposal for implementing WebSocket proxy on port 3105. I should document the steps needed before actually implementing it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## WebSocket 代理改到 3105 端口 - 实施预案\n\n### 第一步：修改 WebSocket 代理配置\n\n```bash\n# 1. 修改 ws-proxy.js\nsed -i 's/PROXY_WS_PORT=3103/PROXY_WS_PORT=3105/g' ~/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js\n\n# 2. 修改服务文件\n# 文件位置: /tmp/openclaw-ws-proxy.service\nEnvironment=\"PROXY_WS_PORT=3105\"\n```\n\n### 第二步：恢复 Gateway 到原始端口\n\n```bash\n# 1. 修改 Gateway 服务文件\n# 文件位置: ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\nExecStart=... gateway --port 18789\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\n\n# 2. 修改前端配置\n# 文件位置: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\"port\": 18789\n```\n\n### 第三步：部署\n\n```bash\n# 1. WebSocket 代理\nsudo cp /tmp/openclaw-ws-proxy.service /etc/systemd/system/\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-ws-proxy\n\n# 2. Gateway\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n### 第四步：验证\n\n| 端口 | 服务 | 验证命令 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 18789 | Gateway | `ss -tlnp \\| grep 18789` |\n| 3103 | HTTP Router | `curl localhost:3102/health` |\n| 3105 | WebSocket 代理 | `curl localhost:3104/health` |\n\n### 架构变化\n\n```\n修改前:\n前端 → 3103 (Gateway)\n\n修改后:\n前端 → 3105 (WebSocket代理+意图判断+评分) → 18789 (Gateway)\n     ↓\n  3102 (HTTP API)\n```\n\n---\n\n**是否执行这个预案？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":721,"output":437,"cacheRead":110464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111622,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775449560758,"responseId":"019d610a555b97d0867cb313a84876ba"}}
