{"type":"message","id":"96da9bad","parentId":"5b035112","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:27:01.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The intent API is working now. The error earlier was probably due to formatting.\n\nNow I have a clear picture:\n\n| Port | Service | Process | Status |\n|------|---------|---------|--------|\n| 3101 | Context API | node (450) | ✅ LISTEN |\n| 3102 | HTTP Router | node (452) | ✅ LISTEN |\n| 3103 | Gateway | openclaw-gateway (3881) | ✅ LISTEN |\n| 3104 | Health Check | node (4338) | ✅ LISTEN |\n| 18789 | - | - | Not listening |\n\nThe Gateway is on 3103, WebSocket proxy on 3104 is not actually listening on 3105, it seems to be using 3104 for health only. Let me verify the ws-proxy process.\n\nActually wait - there's an issue. The ws-proxy is running but it's supposed to be on 3103 or 3105, but the port 3103 is occupied by Gateway. Let me check this more carefully.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前系统状态\n\n| 端口 | 服务 | 进程 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **3101** | Context API | node (450) | ✅ 正常 |\n| **3102** | HTTP Router | node (452) | ✅ 正常 |\n| **3103** | Gateway | openclaw-gateway (3881) | ✅ 正常 |\n| **3104** | 健康检查 | node (4338) | ✅ 正常 |\n| 18789 | - | - | ❌ 未使用 |\n| **3105** | WebSocket代理 | - | ❌ 未运行 |\n\n### 问题\n\n- WebSocket 代理 (ws-proxy) 尝试监听 3103，但被 Gateway 占用\n- 健康检查在 3104，但 ws-proxy 实际没有正确监听 3103\n\n### 结论\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 3105 空闲 | ✅ 可用 |\n| 需要 Gateway 改回 18789 | ✅ 需要 |\n| WebSocket 改到 3105 | ✅ 可行 |\n\n**预案仍然有效**，但目前 HTTP API (3102) 已可正常工作。是否执行？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":113105,"output":464,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775449614118,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3c4f4cb1-061a-453d-8a2f-2af3e0784ae8"}}
