{"type":"message","id":"d14fdd48","parentId":"0847334c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:27:34.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问预案怎么样，让我总结一下预案的完整情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 预案总结\n\n### 目标\n把 WebSocket 代理改到 3105 端口，实现自动意图判断和评分\n\n### 步骤\n\n| 步骤 | 操作 | 文件 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1 | Gateway 改回 18789 | `~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service` |\n| 2 | 前端配置改回 18789 | `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` |\n| 3 | WebSocket 代理改到 3105 | `ws-proxy.js` + 服务文件 |\n| 4 | 部署并验证 | - |\n\n### 架构变化\n\n```\n现在:\n前端 → 3103 (Gateway) — 无意图判断\n\n预案后:\n前端 → 3105 (WebSocket代理+意图判断+评分) → 18789 (Gateway)\n       ↓\n     3102 (HTTP API)\n```\n\n### 风险\n\n| 风险 | 等级 | 应对 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 端口配置混乱 | 中 | 严格按照预案顺序 |\n| Gateway 重启失败 | 低 | 备份现有配置 |\n\n### 结论\n\n✅ **预案可行**，但目前 HTTP API 已可用，WebSocket 代理是**可选优化**。\n\n**建议**：先不执行，继续用 HTTP API (3102) 手动调用即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":113378,"output":293,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113671,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775449646758,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6b21bb36-9d72-4da5-90e0-abd6b9ee7f83"}}
{"type":"message","id":"38971c00","parentId":"d14fdd48","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:34:19.432Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 12:34 GMT+8] 学习、认真全部看一下，进行分析可不可以执行？先回答我：下面提供**增强版监听服务**，新增三个生产级特性：**持久化消息队列**、**LLM 自定义回复**、**健康检查 HTTP 端点**。代码保持高鲁棒性、可配置、可观测。\n\n---\n\n## 📦 安装新增依赖\n\n```bash\ncd ~/openclaw-listener\nnpm install better-sqlite3 express\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 更新配置文件 `config.json`\n\n```json\n{\n \"gateway\": {\n \"url\": \"ws://127.0.0.1:3103\",\n \"token\": \"你的网关令牌\",\n \"heartbeatInterval\": 30000,\n \"reconnect\": {\n \"initialDelay\": 1000,\n \"maxDelay\": 60000,\n \"factor\": 1.5\n }\n },\n \"api\": {\n \"intent\": \"http://localhost:3102/api/intent\",\n \"score\": \"http://localhost:3102/api/score\"\n },\n \"llm\": {\n \"enabled\": false,\n \"provider\": \"openai\",\n \"model\": \"gpt-3.5-turbo\",\n \"apiKey\": \"your-openai-api-key\",\n \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1\",\n \"systemPrompt\": \"You are a helpful assistant.\",\n \"maxTokens\": 150,\n \"temperature\": 0.7\n },\n \"reply\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"mode\": \"template\", // \"template\" 或 \"llm\" 或 \"none\"\n \"template\": \"🤖 意图：{{intent}}，评分：{{score}}\",\n \"llmFallbackTemplate\": \"抱歉，我暂时无法生成回复。\"\n },\n \"behavior\": {\n \"messageField\": \"content\",\n \"queueEnabled\": true, // 启用离线消息队列\n \"queueDbPath\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener-queue.db\"\n },\n \"health\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"port\": 3106,\n \"endpoint\": \"/health\"\n },\n \"logging\": {\n \"level\": \"info\",\n \"file\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener.log\"\n }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧠 增强版 `listener.js`（包含队列、LLM、健康检查）\n\n```javascript\nimport fs from 'node:fs';\nimport path from 'node:path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'node:url';\nimport WebSocket from 'ws';\nimport axios from 'axios';\nimport pino from 'pino';\nimport dotenv from 'dotenv';\nimport Database from 'better-sqlite3';\nimport express from 'express';\n\ndotenv.config();\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\n\n// ---------- 配置加载 ----------\nlet config;\ntry {\n const configPath = path.join(__dirname, 'config.json');\n config = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(configPath, 'utf-8'));\n} catch (err) {\n console.error('无法加载 config.json', err);\n process.exit(1);\n}\n\n// ---------- 日志 ----------\nconst logTransport = config.logging.file\n ? pino.destination({ dest: config.logging.file, sync: false, mkdir: true })\n : process.stdout;\nconst logger = pino(\n { level: config.logging.level, formatters: { level: (label) => ({ level: label }) }, timestamp: pino.stdTimeFunctions.isoTime },\n logTransport\n);\nif (config.logging.file) logger.add(pino.destination(1));\n\n// ---------- 配置校验 ----------\nif (!config.gateway.url || !config.gateway.token) {\n logger.error('缺少 gateway.url 或 gateway.token');\n process.exit(1);\n}\n\n// ---------- 全局状态 ----------\nlet ws = null;\nlet reconnectTimer = null;\nlet reconnectAttempts = 0;\nlet isShuttingDown = false;\nlet healthStatus = { state: 'starting', lastError: null, connected: false, queueSize: 0 };\n\n// ---------- 持久化消息队列 (SQLite) ----------\nlet db = null;\nlet queueStmt = null;\nif (config.behavior.queueEnabled) {\n db = new Database(config.behavior.queueDbPath);\n db.exec(`\n CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS message_queue (\n id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n raw_message TEXT NOT NULL,\n created_at INTEGER NOT NULL\n )\n `);\n queueStmt = {\n insert: db.prepare('INSERT INTO message_queue (raw_message, created_at) VALUES (?, ?)'),\n select: db.prepare('SELECT id, raw_message FROM message_queue ORDER BY created_at LIMIT 10'),\n delete: db.prepare('DELETE FROM message_queue WHERE id = ?'),\n count: db.prepare('SELECT COUNT(*) as count FROM message_queue'),\n };\n logger.info('消息队列已启用');\n}\n\nfunction enqueueMessage(rawMsg) {\n if (!db) return false;\n try {\n queueStmt.insert.run(rawMsg, Date.now());\n updateHealthQueueSize();\n logger.debug({ rawMsg }, '消息已入队');\n return true;\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err }, '消息入队失败');\n return false;\n }\n}\n\nfunction dequeueMessage(id) {\n if (!db) return;\n queueStmt.delete.run(id);\n updateHealthQueueSize();\n}\n\nfunction getQueuedMessages(limit = 10) {\n if (!db) return [];\n return queueStmt.select.all(limit);\n}\n\nfunction updateHealthQueueSize() {\n if (db) {\n const row = queueStmt.count.get();\n healthStatus.queueSize = row.count;\n }\n}\n\nasync function replayQueuedMessages() {\n if (!config.behavior.queueEnabled || !ws || ws.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) return;\n const messages = getQueuedMessages(20);\n if (messages.length === 0) return;\n logger.info({ count: messages.length }, '开始重放离线消息');\n for (const msg of messages) {\n try {\n const parsed = JSON.parse(msg.raw_message);\n await handleMessage(parsed.data || parsed);\n dequeueMessage(msg.id);\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err, msgId: msg.id }, '重放消息失败，保留在队列');\n }\n }\n}\n\n// ---------- LLM 调用 ----------\nasync function callLLM(userMessage, intent, score) {\n if (!config.llm.enabled || config.reply.mode !== 'llm') return null;\n const { provider, model, apiKey, baseUrl, systemPrompt, maxTokens, temperature } = config.llm;\n if (!apiKey) throw new Error('LLM API key 未配置');\n\n const messages = [\n { role: 'system', content: systemPrompt },\n { role: 'user', content: `用户消息：${userMessage}\\n意图：${intent}\\n评分：${score}\\n请生成自然回复。` }\n ];\n\n try {\n let response;\n if (provider === 'openai') {\n const resp = await axios.post(\n `${baseUrl}/chat/completions`,\n { model, messages, max_tokens: maxTokens, temperature },\n { headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiKey}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, timeout: 15000 }\n );\n response = resp.data.choices[0].message.content;\n } else {\n throw new Error(`不支持的 LLM provider: ${provider}`);\n }\n return response;\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err }, 'LLM 调用失败');\n return config.reply.llmFallbackTemplate;\n }\n}\n\n// ---------- API 调用（带重试） ----------\nasync function callWithRetry(fn, maxRetries = 3, delay = 1000) {\n for (let i = 0; i <= maxRetries; i++) {\n try {\n return await fn();\n } catch (err) {\n if (i === maxRetries) throw err;\n logger.warn({ attempt: i + 1, error: err.message }, 'API 调用失败，重试中');\n await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, delay * (i + 1)));\n }\n }\n}\n\nasync function detectIntent(text) {\n const res = await callWithRetry(() => axios.post(config.api.intent, { message: text }, { timeout: 5000 }));\n return res.data;\n}\n\nasync function getScore(text) {\n const res = await callWithRetry(() => axios.get(config.api.score, { params: { task: text }, timeout: 5000 }));\n return res.data;\n}\n\n// ---------- 消息处理核心 ----------\nasync function handleMessage(msgData) {\n const text = msgData[config.behavior.messageField];\n if (!text || typeof text !== 'string') {\n logger.debug({ msgData }, '消息不含有效文本字段');\n return;\n }\n logger.info({ text }, '收到用户消息');\n\n let intent = 'unknown';\n let score = 'N/A';\n try {\n const [intentRes, scoreRes] = await Promise.allSettled([detectIntent(text), getScore(text)]);\n if (intentRes.status === 'fulfilled') intent = intentRes.value.intent;\n if (scoreRes.status === 'fulfilled') score = scoreRes.value.score;\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err }, '意图/评分 API 调用失败');\n }\n logger.info({ text, intent, score }, '分析完成');\n\n // 生成回复\n if (config.reply.enabled && ws && ws.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n let reply = null;\n if (config.reply.mode === 'template') {\n reply = config.reply.template.replace('{{intent}}', intent).replace('{{score}}', String(score));\n } else if (config.reply.mode === 'llm' && config.llm.enabled) {\n reply = await callLLM(text, intent, score);\n }\n if (reply) {\n ws.send(JSON.stringify({ type: 'reply', content: reply }));\n logger.debug({ reply }, '已发送回复');\n }\n }\n}\n\n// ---------- WebSocket 连接管理 ----------\nfunction connectWebSocket() {\n if (isShuttingDown) return;\n const url = `${config.gateway.url}?token=${encodeURIComponent(config.gateway.token)}`;\n logger.info({ url: url.replace(/token=.*/, 'token=***') }, '连接 Gateway');\n\n ws = new WebSocket(url, { handshakeTimeout: 10000, maxPayload: 10 * 1024 * 1024 });\n\n ws.on('open', () => {\n logger.info('WebSocket 已连接');\n reconnectAttempts = 0;\n if (reconnectTimer) clearTimeout(reconnectTimer);\n healthStatus.connected = true;\n healthStatus.lastError = null;\n if (config.gateway.heartbeatInterval) {\n if (ws.heartbeatTimer) clearInterval(ws.heartbeatTimer);\n ws.heartbeatTimer = setInterval(() => { if (ws.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) ws.ping(); }, config.gateway.heartbeatInterval);\n }\n // 重放离线队列\n replayQueuedMessages().catch(err => logger.error({ err }, '重放队列失败'));\n });\n\n ws.on('message', async (data) => {\n try {\n const parsed = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n if (parsed.type === 'message') {\n const msgObj = parsed.data || parsed;\n // 如果 WebSocket 正常，直接处理；如果队列启用且处理失败，则入队\n try {\n await handleMessage(msgObj);\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err }, '处理消息失败，尝试入队');\n if (config.behavior.queueEnabled) enqueueMessage(data.toString());\n }\n }\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error({ err, raw: data.toString().slice(0, 200) }, '解析消息失败');\n }\n });\n\n ws.on('error', (err) => {\n logger.error({ err }, 'WebSocket 错误');\n healthStatus.lastError = err.message;\n });\n\n ws.on('close', (code, reason) => {\n logger.warn({ code, reason: reason.toString() }, '连接关闭');\n healthStatus.connected = false;\n if (ws.heartbeatTimer) clearInterval(ws.heartbeatTimer);\n ws = null;\n if (!isShuttingDown) scheduleReconnect();\n });\n\n ws.on('pong', () => logger.trace('收到 pong'));\n}\n\nfunction scheduleReconnect() {\n if (reconnectTimer) return;\n const delay = Math.min(\n config.gateway.reconnect.initialDelay * Math.pow(config.gateway.reconnect.factor, reconnectAttempts),\n config.gateway.reconnect.maxDelay\n );\n reconnectAttempts++;\n logger.info({ delay, attempt: reconnectAttempts }, '计划重连');\n reconnectTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n reconnectTimer = null;\n connectWebSocket();\n }, delay);\n}\n\n// ---------- 健康检查 HTTP 服务器 ----------\nif (config.health.enabled) {\n const app = express();\n app.get(config.health.endpoint, (req, res) => {\n updateHealthQueueSize();\n const status = {\n status: healthStatus.connected ? 'ok' : 'degraded',\n connected: healthStatus.connected,\n queueSize: healthStatus.queueSize,\n reconnectAttempts,\n lastError: healthStatus.lastError,\n uptime: process.uptime(),\n version: '2.0.0'\n };\n res.json(status);\n });\n app.listen(config.health.port, '127.0.0.1', () => {\n logger.info({ port: config.health.port, endpoint: config.health.endpoint }, '健康检查端点已启动');\n });\n}\n\n// ---------- 优雅退出 ----------\nfunction shutdown() {\n if (isShuttingDown) return;\n isShuttingDown = true;\n logger.info('收到退出信号，正在关闭...');\n if (reconnectTimer) clearTimeout(reconnectTimer);\n if (ws) {\n ws.removeAllListeners();\n if (ws.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) ws.close(1000, 'Shutdown');\n }\n if (db) db.close();\n setTimeout(() => { logger.info('服务已关闭'); process.exit(0); }, 500);\n}\nprocess.on('SIGTERM', shutdown);\nprocess.on('SIGINT', shutdown);\n\n// 定期健康状态日志\nsetInterval(() => {\n updateHealthQueueSize();\n logger.info({ connected: healthStatus.connected, queueSize: healthStatus.queueSize, reconnectAttempts }, '健康状态');\n}, 60000);\n\n// 启动\nconnectWebSocket();\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 部署与测试\n\n### 1. 更新服务文件（如需 systemd）\n\n无需修改，保持原样即可。\n\n### 2. 重启服务\n\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-listener\n```\n\n### 3. 验证健康检查\n\n```bash\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:3106/health\n```\n\n示例响应：\n```json\n{\n \"status\": \"ok\",\n \"connected\": true,\n \"queueSize\": 0,\n \"reconnectAttempts\": 0,\n \"lastError\": null,\n \"uptime\": 123.45,\n \"version\": \"2.0.0\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 测试离线队列\n\n1. 停止 Gateway：`systemctl --user stop openclaw-gateway`\n2. 发送一条消息（通过飞书或任何前端）\n3. 查看日志应出现“消息已入队”\n4. 重启 Gateway：`systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway`\n5. 监听服务应自动重放消息并处理\n\n### 5. 测试 LLM 回复\n\n修改 `config.json`：\n```json\n\"llm\": { \"enabled\": true, \"apiKey\": \"sk-xxx\", ... },\n\"reply\": { \"mode\": \"llm\", ... }\n```\n重启服务后，用户消息会收到 LLM 生成的回复。\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 关键增强点说明\n\n| 特性 | 实现细节 |\n|------|----------|\n| **持久化队列** | better-sqlite3 存储原始消息，重连后自动重放，防止数据丢失 |\n| **LLM 回复** | 支持 OpenAI 兼容接口，可配置 system prompt、model、temperature，失败时回退模板 |\n| **健康检查** | Express 端点 `/health` 提供连接状态、队列积压、重试次数、uptime |\n| **鲁棒性** | 所有异步操作都有 try-catch，队列操作不影响主流程，优雅关闭时清理数据库连接 |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 注意事项\n\n- 消息队列默认存储路径为 `/tmp`，重启会丢失。如需持久化，修改 `queueDbPath` 到非临时目录（如 `/home/ai/.openclaw/listener-queue.db`）。\n- LLM 调用会阻塞消息处理，建议配置较短的 timeout，或改为异步后台任务（可进一步优化为独立 worker）。\n- 健康检查端口 `3106` 可自定义，确保不与其他服务冲突。"}],"timestamp":1775450059421}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7d78675","parentId":"38971c00","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:34:29.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我分析这个增强版监听服务方案，看看是否可以执行。让我仔细分析一下。\n\n这个方案是创建一个独立的监听服务 (listener)，它会：\n1. 连接到 Gateway (3103)\n2. 监听用户消息\n3. 调用意图判断 API (3102)\n4. 调用评分 API (3102)\n5. 生成回复（模板或 LLM）\n6. 通过 WebSocket 发送回复\n\n关键点：\n1. 持久化消息队列 (SQLite)\n2. LLM 自定义回复\n3. 健康检查 HTTP 端点\n\n让我分析可行性：\n\n### 优点\n- 不需要修改 Gateway 代码\n- 独立服务，易于管理\n- 支持离线消息队列\n- 支持 LLM 生成回复\n- 有健康检查\n\n### 需要的前提条件\n1. Gateway 在 3103 端口运行 - ✅ 当前是 3103\n2. 意图判断 API 在 3102 - ✅ 当前正常\n3. 评分 API 在 3102 - ✅ 当前正常\n4. 需要安装新依赖: better-sqlite3, express\n5. 需要配置 config.json\n\n### 潜在问题\n1. 这个服务是监听 Gateway 的 WebSocket，Gateway 需要支持消息监听\n2. 需要 Gateway 的 token\n3. 3106 端口需要空闲\n\n让我检查一下这些前提条件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1cf52981f3fc43929a88ee47","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 分析增强版监听服务方案 ===\" \necho \"\"\n\necho \"【1. 依赖检查】\"\necho \"需要: better-sqlite3, express, axios, pino, dotenv\"\nls ~/openclaw-router/node_modules/ | grep -E \"better-sqlite3|express|axios|pino|dotenv\" || echo \"部分依赖缺失\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【2. 端口检查】\"\nss -tlnp | grep 3106 || echo \"3106 端口可用 ✅\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【3. Gateway WebSocket 检查】\"\necho \"方案需要连接到 Gateway WebSocket 并接收消息\"\necho \"当前 Gateway: ws://127.0.0.1:3103\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【4. API 可用性检查】\"\necho \"意图判断:\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/intent -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"test\"}' | jq '.'\necho \"评分:\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=test\" | jq '.plan.mode'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":117097,"output":532,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117629,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775450059430,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f3caaf5a-e32e-42ef-b0dc-5a6a94709ace"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dea01b32","parentId":"a7d78675","timestamp":"2026-04-06T04:34:29.267Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1cf52981f3fc43929a88ee47","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 分析增强版监听服务方案 ===\n\n【1. 依赖检查】\n需要: better-sqlite3, express, axios, pino, dotenv\naxios\nexpress\n\n【2. 端口检查】\n3106 端口可用 ✅\n\n【3. Gateway WebSocket 检查】\n方案需要连接到 Gateway WebSocket 并接收消息\n当前 Gateway: ws://127.0.0.1:3103\n\n【4. API 可用性检查】\n意图判断:\n{\n  \"isTask\": false,\n  \"confidence\": 0\n}\n评分:\n\"STEP_ARCHIVE\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"=== 分析增强版监听服务方案 ===\n\n【1. 依赖检查】\n需要: better-sqlite3, express, axios, pino, dotenv\naxios\nexpress\n\n【2. 端口检查】\n3106 端口可用 ✅\n\n【3. Gateway WebSocket 检查】\n方案需要连接到 Gateway WebSocket 并接收消息\n当前 Gateway: ws://127.0.0.1:3103\n\n【4. API 可用性检查】\n意图判断:\n{\n  \"isTask\": false,\n  \"confidence\": 0\n}\n评分:\n\"STEP_ARCHIVE\"","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775450069259}}
