{"type":"message","id":"003f85a2","parentId":"60f1b70e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:13:58.305Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_544fcbaa69e6426b99bff899","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 Gateway 状态 ===\n\nLISTEN    0         511               127.0.0.1:3103            0.0.0.0:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=3881,fd=22))                                     \nLISTEN    0         511                   [::1]:3103               [::]:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=3881,fd=23))                                     \n\n【重连测试】\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"connected\": true,\n  \"reconnectAttempts\": 0\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":36,"aggregated":"=== 检查 Gateway 状态 ===\n\nLISTEN    0         511               127.0.0.1:3103            0.0.0.0:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=3881,fd=22))                                     \nLISTEN    0         511                   [::1]:3103               [::]:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=3881,fd=23))                                     \n\n【重连测试】\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"connected\": true,\n  \"reconnectAttempts\": 0\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775452438297}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a9c4634","parentId":"003f85a2","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:14:01.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 正常运行（3103 端口），监听服务状态已恢复 connected: true。看起来是短暂断连后自动重连了。测试结果正常。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 测试结果\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| 监听服务健康 | ✅ ok |\n| Gateway 连接 | ✅ connected |\n| 意图判断 | ✅ isTask=true, confidence=0.5 |\n| 评分 | 20分 → DIRECT |\n\n**测试通过！** 监听服务正常工作，会自动连接 Gateway 并调用意图判断和评分 API。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":149740,"output":114,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775452438306,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f6ee50eb-ec15-4763-b32c-71ad091d4bb3"}}
