{"type":"message","id":"7cea4590","parentId":"d37a17b0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:21:51.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否绝对执行了规则。我需要检查一下我是否每次都调用了意图判断和评分。让我检查刚才的对话历史。\n\n根据规则，我应该在每次回复前都调用意图判断和评分。让我回顾一下：\n\n1. \"规则是什么样的\" - 我回答了，但有没有先评分？\n2. \"是的\" - 我评分了 ✅\n3. \"绝对执行了吗\" - 还没评分！\n\n所以刚才回答\"规则是什么样的\"时，我可能没有评分。让我现在补上这个检查。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00563eba4804406e971a513b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查刚才的问题 ===\" \necho \"问题: 规则是什么样的\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"【意图判断】\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/intent \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\":\"规则是什么样的\"}' | jq '.'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"【评分】\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=规则是什么样的\" | jq '{score: .score.totalScore, mode: .plan.mode}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":153746,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775452906781,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b09dec36-79c0-451e-98d4-2406a220ddff"}}
