{"type":"message","id":"242aca34","parentId":"f1cce2dc","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:25:09.567Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ff58a8866df0479fb781cd33","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 WebSocket 代理 ===\n\n【1】端口监听\nLISTEN    0         511               127.0.0.1:3103            0.0.0.0:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=5524,fd=22))                                     \nLISTEN    0         511                   [::1]:3103               [::]:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=5524,fd=23))                                     \n\n【2】WebSocket 代理进程\nai          4338  0.0  0.4 11512864 66956 ?      Ssl  12:16   0:00 /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node /home/ai/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js\n\n【3】健康检查\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"uptime\": 4102.015668551,\n  \"connections\": 0,\n  \"proxyPort\": 3103,\n  \"gatewayUrl\": \"ws://localhost:3103\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"=== 检查 WebSocket 代理 ===\n\n【1】端口监听\nLISTEN    0         511               127.0.0.1:3103            0.0.0.0:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=5524,fd=22))                                     \nLISTEN    0         511                   [::1]:3103               [::]:*        users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=5524,fd=23))                                     \n\n【2】WebSocket 代理进程\nai          4338  0.0  0.4 11512864 66956 ?      Ssl  12:16   0:00 /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node /home/ai/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js\n\n【3】健康检查\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"uptime\": 4102.015668551,\n  \"connections\": 0,\n  \"proxyPort\": 3103,\n  \"gatewayUrl\": \"ws://localhost:3103\"\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775453109557}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e3fa811","parentId":"242aca34","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:25:25.801Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"WebSocket 代理 (ws-proxy) 是在运行的，但它连接的是 Gateway (3103)，不是意图判断和评分。问题是 ws-proxy 只是转发消息，不会自动调用意图判断和评分。让我解释一下当前架构和问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 分析\n\n### WebSocket 代理现状\n\n| 项目 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ws-proxy 进程 | ✅ 运行中 | 4338 |\n| 监听端口 | 3103 | 但被 Gateway 占用 |\n| gatewayUrl | ws://localhost:3103 | 转发到 Gateway |\n\n### 问题\n\n**WebSocket 代理没有自动意图判断功能！**\n\n之前我们创建的 ws-proxy.py 只是：\n1. 接收消息\n2. 转发到 Gateway\n3. 返回响应\n\n**没有自动调用意图判断和评分 API！**\n\n### 对比\n\n| 方案 | 自动评分 |\n|------|----------|\n| WebSocket 代理 | ❌ 没有 |\n| 监听服务 (openclaw-listener) | ✅ 有，但只是记录日志 |\n\n### 结论\n\n- WebSocket 代理 (ws-proxy) **不自动评分**\n- 监听服务 (openclaw-listener) 会调用 API，但**不会告诉我结果**\n\n**问题在于**：评分结果没有传递给我或用户，只是记录在日志里。\n\n你想让监听服务把评分结果**告诉我**吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1769,"output":282,"cacheRead":153856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155907,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775453109570,"responseId":"019d613fc11879b7d83b61ef14b8d56d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a59d1de","parentId":"2e3fa811","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:31:47.383Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 13:31 GMT+8] 全部观看先评分、分析、怎么执行，先回答我不要进行操作，使用我给你提供的代码执行，只在适配本地的过程中有需要修改的是再进修改：# WebSocket 代理最终增强版：集成意图判断与评分，向前端发送提示\n\n本版本基于之前高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理，增加了**自动任务检测与评分**功能，并将结果实时推送到前端对话界面（作为辅助消息）。所有操作均为异步非阻塞，不影响正常消息转发；具备完整的错误处理、超时控制和降级策略，满足生产环境要求。\n\n---\n\n## 一、核心改进点\n\n1. **消息提取**：兼容多种前端消息格式（`content`, `message`, `text` 等）。\n2. **本地评分**：直接调用已有的 `intentDetector` 和 `scoring` 模块，避免 HTTP 延迟。\n3. **非阻塞**：使用 `setImmediate` 分离评分逻辑，不增加消息转发延迟。\n4. **提示消息发送**：当判定为任务且置信度 >0.5 时，构造一条辅助消息通过 WebSocket 发送回前端（格式与 Gateway 标准输出兼容）。\n5. **防重复发送**：对同一会话中的连续相似消息进行去重（简单缓存）。\n6. **健壮性**：所有异常捕获、超时控制、降级处理，评分模块失败不影响主链路。\n7. **可配置**：支持通过环境变量禁用提示、调整超时、去重窗口等。\n\n---\n\n## 二、完整代码（`ws-proxy.js`）\n\n```javascript\n// ws-proxy.js\n// 高鲁棒 WebSocket 代理 + 自动任务评分 + 实时提示\n// 版本: 2.0.0\n\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst { detectIntent } = require('./intentDetector'); // 本地意图判断模块\nconst { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan } = require('./scoring'); // 本地评分模块\n\n// ========== 配置（支持环境变量） ==========\nconst CONFIG = {\n gatewayWsUrl: process.env.OPENCLAW_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:18789', // 原 Gateway 端口\n proxyPort: parseInt(process.env.PROXY_WS_PORT || '3103', 10),\n heartbeatIntervalMs: parseInt(process.env.HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS || '30000', 10),\n connectionTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.CONNECTION_TIMEOUT_MS || '10000', 10),\n maxReconnectAttempts: parseInt(process.env.MAX_RECONNECT_ATTEMPTS || '5', 10),\n reconnectBaseDelayMs: parseInt(process.env.RECONNECT_BASE_DELAY_MS || '1000', 10),\n maxCachedMessages: parseInt(process.env.MAX_CACHED_MESSAGES || '100', 10),\n maxMessageSizeBytes: parseInt(process.env.MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE_BYTES || '1048576', 10), // 1MB\n enableRateLimit: process.env.ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT === 'true',\n rateLimitPerSec: parseInt(process.env.RATE_LIMIT_PER_SEC || '10', 10),\n healthPort: parseInt(process.env.HEALTH_PORT || '3104', 10),\n // 新增：评分相关配置\n enableScoring: process.env.ENABLE_SCORING !== 'false', // 默认开启\n scoringTimeoutMs: parseInt(process.env.SCORING_TIMEOUT_MS || '2000', 10),\n sendHint: process.env.SEND_HINT !== 'false', // 默认发送提示\n hintCooldownMs: parseInt(process.env.HINT_COOLDOWN_MS || '5000', 10), // 同会话同任务冷却时间\n};\n\n// ========== 辅助函数 ==========\nconst log = (level, msg, meta = {}) => {\n console[level](`[WSProxy] ${msg}`, meta);\n};\n\n// 提取用户文本（支持多种格式）\nconst messageExtractors = [\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.content || p.message || p.text; } catch(e) {} },\n (data) => { try { const p = JSON.parse(data); return p.data?.message || p.data?.text; } catch(e) {} },\n];\nfunction extractUserMessage(data) {\n for (const extractor of messageExtractors) {\n const result = extractor(data);\n if (result && typeof result === 'string') return result.trim();\n }\n return null;\n}\n\n// 简单速率限制（令牌桶）\nclass RateLimiter {\n constructor(tokensPerSec) {\n this.tokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.maxTokens = tokensPerSec;\n this.lastRefill = Date.now();\n }\n allow() {\n const now = Date.now();\n const elapsed = (now - this.lastRefill) / 1000;\n this.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, this.tokens + elapsed * this.maxTokens);\n this.lastRefill = now;\n if (this.tokens >= 1) {\n this.tokens -= 1;\n return true;\n }\n return false;\n }\n}\n\n// 去重缓存（简单 LRU）\nclass SimpleCache {\n constructor(maxSize = 100, ttlMs = 60000) {\n this.cache = new Map();\n this.maxSize = maxSize;\n this.ttl = ttlMs;\n }\n set(key, value) {\n if (this.cache.size >= this.maxSize) {\n const oldest = this.cache.keys().next().value;\n this.cache.delete(oldest);\n }\n this.cache.set(key, { value, expires: Date.now() + this.ttl });\n }\n get(key) {\n const entry = this.cache.get(key);\n if (!entry) return null;\n if (Date.now() > entry.expires) {\n this.cache.delete(key);\n return null;\n }\n return entry.value;\n }\n}\n\n// ========== WebSocket 代理客户端类 ==========\nclass WSProxyClient {\n constructor(clientSocket, req) {\n this.clientSocket = clientSocket;\n this.clientAddr = req.socket.remoteAddress;\n this.clientId = crypto.randomUUID();\n this.gatewaySocket = null;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n this.pendingMessages = [];\n this.connected = false;\n this.rateLimiter = CONFIG.enableRateLimit ? new RateLimiter(CONFIG.rateLimitPerSec) : null;\n this.hintCache = new SimpleCache(200, CONFIG.hintCooldownMs); // 防止重复提示\n this.init();\n }\n\n init() {\n this.connectToGateway();\n this.setupClientHandlers();\n }\n\n connectToGateway() {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connecting to Gateway ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl} (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts+1})`);\n this.gatewaySocket = new WebSocket(CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl, {\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n });\n \n const timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket.readyState !== WebSocket.OPEN) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway connection timeout`);\n this.gatewaySocket.terminate();\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n }\n }, CONFIG.connectionTimeoutMs);\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('open', () => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = true;\n this.reconnectAttempts = 0;\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Connected to Gateway`);\n while (this.pendingMessages.length) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(this.pendingMessages.shift());\n }\n this.startHeartbeat();\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('message', (data, isBinary) => {\n if (this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.clientSocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n }\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n\n this.gatewaySocket.on('close', (code, reason) => {\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n this.connected = false;\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Gateway closed: ${code} ${reason || ''}`);\n this.scheduleReconnect();\n });\n }\n\n scheduleReconnect() {\n if (this.reconnectAttempts >= CONFIG.maxReconnectAttempts) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Max reconnects, closing client`);\n this.clientSocket.close();\n return;\n }\n this.reconnectAttempts++;\n const delay = CONFIG.reconnectBaseDelayMs * Math.pow(1.5, this.reconnectAttempts - 1);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Reconnect in ${delay}ms (attempt ${this.reconnectAttempts})`);\n setTimeout(() => this.connectToGateway(), delay);\n }\n\n startHeartbeat() {\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n this.heartbeatTimer = setInterval(() => {\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.ping();\n }\n }, CONFIG.heartbeatIntervalMs);\n }\n\n stopHeartbeat() {\n if (this.heartbeatTimer) {\n clearInterval(this.heartbeatTimer);\n this.heartbeatTimer = null;\n }\n }\n\n // 异步评分并发送提示\n async evaluateAndHint(userText) {\n if (!CONFIG.enableScoring) return;\n const cacheKey = `${this.clientId}:${userText.slice(0, 100)}`;\n if (this.hintCache.get(cacheKey)) return; // 冷却期内不重复提示\n\n try {\n // 1. 意图判断（快速过滤）\n const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userText, null, null);\n if (!isTask || confidence < 0.5) return;\n\n // 2. 详细评分（带超时保护）\n const scorePromise = computeFineScore(userText);\n const timeoutPromise = new Promise((_, reject) =>\n setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Scoring timeout')), CONFIG.scoringTimeoutMs)\n );\n const { totalScore, factors } = await Promise.race([scorePromise, timeoutPromise]);\n const plan = getExecutionPlan(totalScore, factors.scaleIndex);\n\n // 3. 构造提示消息（模仿 AI 回复格式）\n const hintText = `[系统] 检测到任务，评分 ${totalScore}，建议使用 ${plan.mode} 模式（超时 ${plan.timeoutSec || plan.stepTimeoutSec || '?'} 秒）。`;\n const hintMessage = JSON.stringify({\n type: 'assistant',\n content: hintText,\n // 可选：添加额外标识避免与正常回复混淆\n metadata: { source: 'task-scoring' }\n });\n\n // 4. 发送提示到前端\n if (CONFIG.sendHint && this.clientSocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.clientSocket.send(hintMessage);\n this.hintCache.set(cacheKey, true);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Sent scoring hint: ${hintText.slice(0, 80)}...`);\n }\n } catch (err) {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Scoring failed: ${err.message}`);\n }\n }\n\n setupClientHandlers() {\n this.clientSocket.on('message', async (data, isBinary) => {\n // 速率限制\n if (this.rateLimiter && !this.rateLimiter.allow()) {\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Rate limit exceeded`);\n return;\n }\n\n // 提取用户消息（非阻塞评分）\n const userText = extractUserMessage(data);\n if (userText) {\n setImmediate(() => this.evaluateAndHint(userText));\n }\n\n // 转发到 Gateway\n if (this.connected && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.send(data, { binary: isBinary });\n } else {\n this.pendingMessages.push(data);\n if (this.pendingMessages.length > CONFIG.maxCachedMessages) {\n this.pendingMessages.shift();\n log('warn', `[${this.clientId}] Message cache full, dropped oldest`);\n }\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('close', () => {\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Client disconnected`);\n this.stopHeartbeat();\n if (this.gatewaySocket && this.gatewaySocket.readyState === WebSocket.OPEN) {\n this.gatewaySocket.close();\n }\n });\n\n this.clientSocket.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `[${this.clientId}] Client error: ${err.message}`);\n });\n }\n}\n\n// ========== 启动 WebSocket 代理服务器 ==========\nconst wss = new WebSocket.Server({\n port: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n maxPayload: CONFIG.maxMessageSizeBytes,\n});\n\nwss.on('connection', (clientSocket, req) => {\n log('info', `New client from ${req.socket.remoteAddress}`);\n new WSProxyClient(clientSocket, req);\n});\n\nwss.on('error', (err) => {\n log('error', `WebSocket server error: ${err.message}`);\n});\n\nlog('info', `WebSocket proxy listening on port ${CONFIG.proxyPort}, forwarding to ${CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl}`);\n\n// ========== 健康检查 HTTP 服务 ==========\nconst express = require('express');\nconst healthApp = express();\nhealthApp.get('/health', (req, res) => {\n res.json({\n status: 'ok',\n uptime: process.uptime(),\n connections: wss.clients.size,\n config: {\n proxyPort: CONFIG.proxyPort,\n gatewayUrl: CONFIG.gatewayWsUrl,\n scoringEnabled: CONFIG.enableScoring,\n }\n });\n});\nhealthApp.listen(CONFIG.healthPort, () => {\n log('info', `Health check on port ${CONFIG.healthPort}`);\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、部署与测试\n\n### 1. 安装依赖（如果尚未安装）\n```bash\ncd /opt/openclaw-router\nnpm install ws express\n```\n\n### 2. 确保 `intentDetector.js` 和 `scoring.js` 存在（根据之前实现）\n这两个模块已在前序步骤中创建，只需保证路径正确。\n\n### 3. 停止旧代理（如有）\n```bash\nsudo systemctl stop openclaw-ws-proxy\npkill -f ws-proxy.js\n```\n\n### 4. 启动新代理\n```bash\nnode /opt/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js &\n```\n或通过 systemd 重启：\n```bash\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-ws-proxy\n```\n\n### 5. 验证\n- 健康检查：`curl http://localhost:3104/health`\n- 发送一条任务消息（如“帮我写个排序函数”），您会收到类似 `[系统] 检测到任务，评分 45，建议使用 SPAWN_SUBAGENT 模式...` 的提示。\n\n### 6. 回退方案\n如果提示消息干扰正常对话，可以设置环境变量 `SEND_HINT=false` 重启代理，或修改 `CONFIG.sendHint = false`。\n\n---\n\n## 四、质量保证与鲁棒性说明\n\n| 维度 | 实现 |\n|------|------|\n| **非阻塞** | 评分逻辑使用 `setImmediate`，消息转发无额外延迟 |\n| **超时控制** | 评分操作 2 秒超时，避免阻塞事件循环 |\n| **错误隔离** | 评分失败只记录日志，不影响主链路 |\n| **去重** | 同一客户端对相似消息在冷却期内只提示一次 |\n| **速率限制** | 可选的令牌桶限流，防止恶意高频消息 |\n| **重连机制** | Gateway 断开后自动重连（指数退避），缓存消息 |\n| **内存控制** | 消息缓存队列限制 100 条，去重缓存自动 LRU |\n| **配置灵活** | 所有关键参数支持环境变量，无需修改代码 |\n| **可观测** | 结构化日志 + 健康检查端点 |\n\n---"}],"timestamp":1775453507369}}
